# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:18
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_d34b3dc7:

    # "My alarm blares into my ears, only to be swiftly silenced by my fist."
    "目覚ましの音が耳に鳴り響く。それを自分の拳で直ちに黙らせる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:23
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_3db1ac03:

    # "My body switches into auto-mode, carrying my subconscious self out of bed and into my uniform."
    "俺の体は自動運転に切り替わり、ぼやけた意識のままベッドから這い出すと、制服に着替える。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:25
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_2b3ffa6b:

    # "As always, my bottles of pills sit on my desk patiently, waiting for me to take them and pick out my daily dosage of medicine; seventeen pills a day."
    "いつものように薬の瓶が机の上に鎮座し、俺が瓶を手に取り１日の服用量として決められている１７錠の錠剤を取り出すのを待っている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:30
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_a5cc44de:

    # "Before I know it, I'm opening the door to class 3-3, glad to see that I'm not the only one who seems to be a little hung-over from festival week."
    "気がつくと俺は３－３のドアを開けている。学園祭週間の疲れが残っている人間が自分だけではないということがわかり嬉しくなる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:32
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_4abd7b7a:

    # "Every face in the classroom looks gaunt. With the festival now over, it's as if everyone's life dreams have been achieved."
    "教室の中にある顔はみんな寂しい感じだ。学園祭が終わって、まるで一生の夢を達成してしまったかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:34
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_4a4c290b:

    # "With nothing left to live for, the students have relied on instincts alone to guide them to class."
    "学園祭という学校生活の中での生き甲斐がなくなり、生徒たちは授業に出るという本能だけを頼りに教室にやってきている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:36
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_e960e014:

    # "Or maybe I'm just reading too much into it."
    "ただの深読みかもしれないけどな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:38
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_3d74beca:

    # "I slowly make my way to my seat, and it's only then that I realize why the room is so peaceful."
    "俺はゆっくりと自分の席に向かうが、ようやくその時、なぜ教室がこんなに静かであるかがわかる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:40
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_c94787db:

    # "The seats beside mine are blissfully empty; the world's loudest interpreter for the deaf has yet to arrive."
    "ありがたいことに、俺の隣の席には誰も座っていない。世界で一番うるさい手話通訳者はまだお着きになっていないようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:52
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_d1d3ccce:

    # "Just as I am about to sit down, the door flies open, revealing a resplendent Misha; drills bobbing from the dramatic entrance and arms stretched towards the sky."
    "俺が腰を下ろそうとしたまさにそのとき、ドアが飛ぶような速度で開き、まばゆく輝くミーシャの姿が現れる。劇的な登場で髪のドリルをピョンピョンと縦に揺らし、両腕を天へと突き出しながら。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:57
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_6660b1d8:

    # mi "Ya-hooo~! It's all over!"
    mi "いやっほーう！　終わったねー！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:59
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_da93f82d:

    # "It would appear that not everyone is affected by the post-festival depression."
    "みんながみんな、学園祭の後の憂鬱に苦しんでいるわけではないみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:61
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_b5183643:

    # "The rest of the class glare at her, obviously thinking the same thing I am."
    "他の生徒全員がミーシャをにらみつける。明らかにみんな俺と同じことを考えているな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:66
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_70b33264:

    # "Misha, still frozen in the doorway with her arms still in the air, nervously looks around."
    "いまだ腕を上へと伸ばした姿勢で教室の入り口で固まったままのミーシャが、心配そうに辺りを見回す。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:68
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_127010a0:

    # "It's obvious that she senses the foul mood, but can't work out exactly what to do."
    "このいやな雰囲気を感じ取っているのは間違いないけど、どうしていいのかわからないでいる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:73
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_5007ba21:

    # "Suddenly, she jerks forward."
    "突然、ミーシャが前へとつんのめる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:78
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_4ed09e68:

    # mi "Hey!"
    mi "あっ！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:88
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_cdd50267:

    # "As she stumbles into the classroom, she reveals Shizune, arm still extended from where she shoved Misha."
    "ミーシャが教室の中へとよろめき、静音の姿が現れる。その腕はミーシャを教室に押し込んだために伸ばされているままだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:93
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:95
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_42ea6a1a:

    # hi "Thanks for the entertainment, but shouldn't you two take your seats?"
    hi "余興をありがとう。でも、二人とも席に着いたほうがいいんじゃないのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:100
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:102
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_f761e4a5:

    # "Still slightly embarrassed, Misha takes a few seconds to realize she has to translate."
    "まだわずかに混乱しているミーシャは、一拍置いて自分が通訳しなければいけないことに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:107
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_7c4aaea2:

    # mi "Oh! Yeah! Shicchan says she's not happy with you ditching us last week."
    mi "そうだよ！　先週ひっちゃんがばっくれたから怒ってる、ってしっちゃんが言ってるよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:112
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_aee22e6f:

    # mi "We were really busy!"
    mi "本当に忙しかったんだから！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:114
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_b6ed210a:

    # hi "Is that so? What about the stuff I already did for you two?"
    hi "そうかよ。俺が二人のために資材を探してやったのはどうなったんだ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:119
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:124
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_0886efc2:

    # mi "She says that only counts for council members. Since you declined, she doesn’t owe you anything."
    mi "生徒会のメンバーじゃなきゃカウントしない、って言ってるよ。ひっちゃんは入会しなかったから、しっちゃんとは何の貸し借りもないの"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:129
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_5113a755:

    # "Misha leans closer, and whispers conspiratorially into my ear."
    "ミーシャが俺に近寄ってきて、陰謀を告げるかのように俺に耳打ちしてくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:131
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_3ac3ec9b:

    # mi "Actually, I think she's just a little sore that you didn’t spend the day with her."
    mi "本当はね、しっちゃんは学園祭でひっちゃんが一緒にいてあげなかったからちょっと不機嫌なだけだと思うよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:136
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_31997731:

    # mi "She's really thankful for your work last week though."
    mi "あんなこと言ってるけど、しっちゃんはひっちゃんが先週手伝ってくれたことに本当に感謝してるんだからね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:141
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_ff8ca9e8:

    # "Sensing that she is being talked about, Shizune lightly raps her fingers on her desk until Misha turns around to face her."
    "自分のことを言われていると気がついたのか、静音はミーシャが自分のほうに顔を向けるまで机を指で叩き続ける。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:155
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_e15ea550:

    # "I can't understand any of the fast-paced signing that's going on, but from Shizune's slightly embarrassed expression, and Misha's poorly contained laughter, I can guess."
    "静音とミーシャのあいだで交わされているペースの速い手話は俺には理解できないけど、静音のわずかに恥ずかしがった表情とミーシャのこらえきれていない笑いからその内容は想像できる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:159
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_7765f059:

    # "While this exchange is happening, the door opens once again, but this time at a much more reasonable pace."
    "そうしている間にドアが再び開く。さっきに比べれば、開く速度はずっとまともだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:172
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_67536029:

    # "Hanako quietly enters the room, and pulls the door closed behind her."
    "華子が静かに部屋に入ってきて、後ろ手でドアを閉める。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:177
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_403e96ca:

    # "Peering out from under her hair, she quickly scans the classroom."
    "華子は髪の下から素早く教室を見渡した。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:179
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_96a6932e:

    # "Our eyes meet, and she suddenly stiffens. She closes her eyes, takes a deep breath, and then walks over to my desk."
    "俺と視線が合うと華子は身体をこわばらせる。そして瞳を閉じて深呼吸を一度してから、俺の机のほうへ歩いてくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:184
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_a2f9183d:

    # ha "G… good morning Hisao."
    ha "お……おはよう、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:186
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_5b914455:

    # hi "Morning Hanako. You're a little late, aren't you?"
    hi "おはよう華子。今日は少し遅いんだな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:191
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_8c4f89fb:

    # ha "I… was talking to Lilly."
    ha "り……リリーと話してたから"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:196
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_2cee45b2:

    # ha "A-about today."
    ha "き、今日のことで"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:198
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_5fbba3d5:

    # hi "Ah, so you've got her list then? We can leave straight after classes in that case."
    hi "ああ、じゃあもうリリーから買い物リストはもらってきたんだね？　それなら授業が終わったらまっすぐ行けるな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:203
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_ff70d1cd:

    # ha "S-sure."
    ha "う、うん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:205
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_81d7ddc4:

    # hi "I'm looking forward to it."
    hi "楽しみにしてるよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:207
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_8c16f8fe:

    # "Hanako briefly flashes her embarrassed smile at me then hurries off to her seat."
    "華子は恥ずかしそうな笑みを一瞬浮かべ、慌てて自分の席のほうへ行ってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:214
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_49e513b4:

    # "During classes, it becomes apparent that it's not only the students that are a little despondent after the festival."
    "授業になって、学園祭の後に意気消沈しているのは生徒だけではないことがわかる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:216
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_ec20446d:

    # "Mutou simply gives us a list of exercises from the textbook and then sits behind his desk."
    "武藤先生は教科書の課題をいくつか俺たちに出しただけで、教卓の後ろに座ってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:218
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_036dbbfd:

    # "I totally forget about the brief lunch period for a moment, such is the banality of the day."
    "あまりに一日が平凡なので、一瞬とはいえ短い昼休みのことまで完全に忘れてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:222
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_85f18f01:

    # "It's mind-numbing, and everyone seems surprised when the bells signal the end of the lessons."
    "退屈でつまらない一日が過ぎる。授業の終わりを告げるチャイムが鳴り、みんな驚いているようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:228
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_70afce89:

    # "As I am packing up my bags, Shizune and Misha flank and entrap me."
    "かばんに勉強道具を詰めていると、静音とミーシャが俺を両脇から捕まえる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:233
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_30516337:

    # mi "Say, Hicchan, it's still not too late to join up. There's a lot of post-festival paperwork for us to complete…"
    mi "ねぇ、ひっちゃん。生徒会に入るの、今ならまだ遅くないよ。書かなきゃいけない学園祭の書類がたくさんあって……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:235
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_945cd433:

    # hi "Er, sorry Misha, I've… got plans…"
    hi "あー悪いなミーシャ、その……今日はもう予定が…………"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:248
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_85efd206:

    # "As if sensing the cue, Hanako appears behind me, holding a small bag, and trying to avoid eye contact with the outside world."
    "そんな合図の意味を理解するかのように、小さなかばんを持った華子が俺の後ろで外界の誰とも目を合わせないようにしながら立っている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:253
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_ae439be9:

    # "Misha's eyes open wide, then she bursts into laughter."
    "ミーシャは目を大きく見開き、どっと笑いだす。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:255
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_99e7d9a4:

    # mi "BWAHAHA! You move fast, don't you Hicchan~? We won't disturb your date any further! Bwahahaha!"
    mi "ぶわっはっは！　行動がお早いようで、ねぇひっちゃん～？　デートの邪魔なんていたしませんよ！　ぶわっはっはっは！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:260
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_ed875abf:

    # "Behind the roaring Misha, I see Shizune taking far too little interest in the scene. I might be taking this the wrong way, but I think she's deliberately ignoring me."
    "爆笑しているミーシャの後ろで、静音が全く興味なさげにしている。俺の思い違いかもしれないけど、静音はわざと俺を無視しているように感じる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:265
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_3ba2957a:

    # "I feel a gentle tug on my shirt, and turn to see Hanako's eyes fixed firmly on the floor."
    "シャツが控えめに引っ張られるのを感じ、俺は床に視線をしっかりと固定したままの華子の目を見るために振り返る。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:270
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_41de7974:

    # ha "L… let's…"
    ha "い……いこう……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:272
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_9c2637a9:

    # hi "Got ya. Shizune, Misha, I'll see you later."
    hi "わかった。静音、ミーシャ、またな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:274
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_283a2529:

    # hi "And I'm still not interested in the council."
    hi "それから、やっぱり生徒会には興味ないから"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:279
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_a6d0047f:

    # mi "Spoilsport."
    mi "つまんないの"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:291
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_8ac4355e:

    # "Misha and Shizune retreat into the hallway, happily signing to each other."
    "ミーシャと静音は楽しそうに手話を交わしながら廊下へ出ていく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:293
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_2f3459cb:

    # hi "Got all your stuff? Let's head off."
    hi "忘れ物はないな？　じゃあ行くか"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:300
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_411c47d4:

    # "Floods of students pour out of the school gates and onto the road into town."
    "生徒たちの大群が校門をくぐり、町へと向かう道へ流れ出ていく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:302
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_8957b27b:

    # "It's a little weird. It's almost a scene from any other high school, but the illusion fades because of the occasional wheelchair or missing limb."
    "ちょっと変な感じだ。この光景は他の高校とほとんど変わらない。しかしときたま目に映る車椅子や手足を欠損した生徒がそんな幻想をかき消す。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:304
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_e5617b90:

    # "One thing I do notice is that nobody is alone."
    "１つ気づいたのは、誰一人として一人きりの人間がいないことだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:312
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_d1edea69:

    # "And, as Hanako and I pass through the gates, I notice that she closes the distance between us."
    "そして華子と一緒に校門をくぐったとき、華子が俺との距離を縮めていることに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:314
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_fda84fd1:

    # "Not enough to be considered 'close', but she certainly isn't at her usual just-a-little-far position."
    "『近づいている』と言えるほどその距離が縮まっているとは思わないけど、いつものちょっと身を引いた距離と違うのは確かだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:316
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_f6e4d131:

    # "I guess we're not familiar enough for her to get as close as she does with Lilly."
    "華子がリリーと親密なほどには、俺と華子の仲は親しくなっていないんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:318
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_381fc1d0:

    # "However, even though she has moved a little closer to me physically, mentally she seems to have traveled a mile."
    "でも、華子が物理的に俺に少し近づいたとしたら、精神的には１キロ近づいているようなものだろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:320
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_2629b5e4:

    # "Her hands clutched around the leather straps of her bag to the point of whitening her knuckles, her head down and her mouth pursed closed."
    "かばんの革紐をつかむ華子の手は、真っ白になるほど強く握られていて、頭も下を向いて口を閉じたままだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:322
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_ac1e1bbc:

    # "She almost looks like she's being walked to the Principal's office for the first time."
    "まるで初めて校長室に行かされているかのように見える。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:324
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_6faefa45:

    # "I try to stifle a giggle at the thought, but it is futile."
    "俺はこんな考えに吹き出してしまいそうになるのをこらえようとするが、その努力は無駄になった。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:329
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_f84a0570:

    # ha "W-what's the matter…?"
    ha "ど、どうかしたの……？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:331
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_38ca3a9b:

    # "I guess there's no point in hiding it…"
    "隠してもしかたないか……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:333
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_c7694a4e:

    # hi "Sorry. For a second there it looked like you were getting in trouble."
    hi "ごめんごめん。ちょっと叱られに行く子どもみたいに見えたからさ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:338
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_4022a22c:

    # ha "W-w-what do you mean?"
    ha "ど、ど、どういうこと？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:340
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_d6240147:

    # hi "I think you need to relax a little. We're not going too far, and it's only students around, right?"
    hi "もう少しリラックスしたほうがいいと思うんだよね。そんなに遠くに行くわけじゃないんだし、周りには山久の生徒しかいないんだからさ。な？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:345
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_40ca9b49:

    # ha "R-right."
    ha "そ、そうだね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:347
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_f0b09cf8:

    # "It bothers me a little to see Hanako so worked up."
    "こんなに華子が取り乱しているのを見ると、ちょっと心配になる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:349
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_fe6a1ad1:

    # hi "And you do this every week, don't you?"
    hi "毎週こうして買いものに行っているんだってな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:354
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_8e898ada:

    # ha "Y-yes. With Lilly."
    ha "う、うん。リリーと"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:356
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_fb1f122d:

    # "Of course. 'With Lilly.' I wonder, has she ever left the school without her?"
    "そうだった。『リリーと』だった。華子はリリーの付き添いなしで学校から出たことはあるんだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:358
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_dd8eb15b:

    # "It doesn't seem like much at first glance, but Hanako's dependence on Lilly is absurdly heavy."
    "一見しただけでは大したことはなさそうだけど、華子のリリーへの依存は途方もなく大きい。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:360
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_51304730:

    # "If she can't even handle leaving the school without her, how would she have managed to survive if the two had never met?"
    "もしリリーがいないと学校の外にさえ出られないのだとしたら、リリーと出会っていなかったらどうやって生きてこられたのだろうか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:362
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_6473c3eb:

    # "Would she have found someone else to latch on to? And what drew her to Lilly?"
    "しがみつく人間を他に見つけていただろうか？　そして、華子をリリーに引き寄せたものはなんだろう？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:364
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_16335268:

    # "Was it her lack of eyesight, or was Lilly just kind enough to lend a hand?"
    "目が見えなかったことか？　それともリリーが色々手を貸してくれる親切な人間だったからか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:366
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_c640fc5d:

    # "I wonder if anyone would have fit the bill."
    "この条件に当てはまる人間は他にいないんじゃないか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:368
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_74edf894:

    # hi "Well, I'm here. Besides, we're not going far. It'll be over before you know it."
    hi "その、なんだ。今日は俺がいるし。それに遠くに行くわけじゃないんだから、気づいたら終わってるって"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:373
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_e56341d7:

    # "Hanako's knuckles slowly regain their color as she tries to hide a small smile, but the effort of that seems to prevent further conversation."
    "華子の拳が徐々にその色を取り戻すのと同時に、彼女は小さな微笑みを隠そうとする。だけどその努力がこれ以上会話が続くことを妨げているように感じられる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:375
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_be891b4e:

    # "We travel, side by side, down the winding road towards the town. The crowd of students thins as we continue along the sidewalk."
    "俺たちは町へと続く曲がりくねった道を並んで下っていく。歩道を進んでいくと生徒の集団が小さくなっていく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:377
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_a5b1b7ba:

    # "Faster students rush ahead, and the less mobile ones fall behind, rarefying the crowd into nothingness."
    "足の速い生徒たちが前へとどんどん突き進み、ゆっくり進む生徒を追い抜いて行くことで集団は分散していき、やがて『集団』とは呼べなくなる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:382
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_10c37307:

    # "By the time we reach the convenience store we are practically alone."
    "俺たちがコンビニに着くころにはほとんど二人だけになる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:387
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_61eb7fc0:

    # "Using me as a shield between herself and the attendant, Hanako moves through the narrow aisles, adding an assortment of items to her basket."
    "華子は俺を店員とのあいだを隔てる壁にして、カゴに商品を入れながら細い通路を進んでいく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:389
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_d0ae944a:

    # "Bread, milk, tea… thyme?"
    "パン、牛乳、紅茶……タイム？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:391
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_b57613d1:

    # "What kind of convenience store sells herbs?"
    "ハーブを売ってるコンビニって、なんだそれ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:395
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:399
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_69982a8b:

    # n "{vspace=60}Then again, nothing about this town seems normal, which may not be such a bad thing in retrospect."
    n "\n\nとはいったものの、思い返してみるとこの町に『普通な』ところなどないようだけど、それは悪い意味のものじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:401
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_d0237add:

    # n "Everything is so different and uncomfortable; dwelling on such matters isn't really an option."
    n "あらゆるものがあまりに違っていて落ち着かない。だからそんなことをくよくよ考えているのはあまりいい選択肢じゃない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:403
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_145e9169:

    # n "When I think about that, it reminds me of Hanako."
    n "なんて思考をめぐらせていると、華子のことが頭に浮かぶ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:405
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_b691319e:

    # n "No matter how much you try, you can't escape her scars; they still interrupt my train of thought when I see them."
    n "どうしたって華子の傷跡からは逃げることはできない。俺も目に入るとまだ気を取られてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:407
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_461b57c4:

    # n "As much as I don't want to admit it to myself, I think I'm forcing myself to try to ignore them."
    n "認めたくないけど、俺は彼女の傷を無理やり無視しようとしているのだと思う。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:409
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_2c78ea94:

    # n "Not that I am scar-free myself. The jagged line down my sternum will never completely fade away."
    n "かといって、俺だって傷なしっていうわけじゃない。胸の上にギザギザに走る手術跡が完全になくなることは決してない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:411
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_7db0e9ae:

    # n "I just have the luxury of being able to hide it easily."
    n "だけど俺の場合は簡単にそれを隠すことができる。華子に比べると贅沢なことだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:413
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_2be61d50:

    # n "{vspace=30}But, in a way, both of our scars remind me that we're all in this place for a reason."
    n "\nでもある意味では、俺と華子の傷跡は俺たちがみんな理由があってこの場所にいるんだということを思い出させてくれる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:418
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_00e4ae06:

    # nvl clear
    # "…"
    nvl clear
    "……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:422
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_d820fab6:

    # "Hanako throws one last item into her basket then sheepishly holds it out to me, along with a few bank notes."
    "華子は買い物リストに残った最後の一品をカゴへ入れ、数枚のお札と一緒におずおずと俺に差し出す。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:427
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_065a8266:

    # ha "C-c-could you p-please…"
    ha "あ、あ、あの、これ、お願い……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:429
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_310f0eb4:

    # "It takes me a second to understand what she's trying to say."
    "華子が言いたいことを理解するのに少し時間がかかる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:431
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_e8a86c24:

    # hi "Oh, you want me to pay for this?"
    hi "ああ、会計してほしいってことか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:436
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_b5a726a4:

    # "She nods, but doesn't look up."
    "華子はうなずくけど、顔を上げない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:438
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_ba3929f3:

    # "I guess this task falls to Lilly on the usual occasions."
    "いつもならこれはリリーの役目なんだな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:440
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_75a6f24a:

    # hi "Sure. Lemme just grab a couple of things…"
    hi "もちろんいいよ。ちょっとだけ待ってて、俺もまだ少し買うから……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:442
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_38b24da6:

    # "Hastily I grab a few essential items for myself and head for the counter with Hanako in close tow."
    "自分用に生活必需品を急いで数個つかむと、後ろに華子を連れてレジへと向かう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:444
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_66d7256e:

    # "The attendant gives me an indifferent nod as he scans in the items."
    "店員は無関心な会釈をして、品物をスキャンする。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:446
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_fa2bc676:

    # "I suppose just ignoring us is one way to deal with the anomalies of Yamaku; they must get a lot of students here, being the closest store to the school."
    "俺たちを無視するというのは、山久の特殊さに対処する１つの方法なんだろう。学校に一番近い店だし、たくさんの生徒が来店するに違いない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:448
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_64ed741c:

    # "The staff must all have their own way of dealing with us. Or maybe they don't; maybe it's only me who thinks twice about my unique schoolmates."
    "ここの店員は皆それぞれが、生徒に対処するその人なりの方法を持っているに違いない。いや、そんなことはないのかもしれない。俺が独特な学友たちについて意識し過ぎているのかもしれないな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:455
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_ddc60390:

    # "Our transaction complete, Hanako and I head back out onto the street."
    "会計が終わり、華子と俺は元来た道へと戻る。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:462
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_21cc1ef3:

    # "The road is pretty much abandoned now. The students that were heading out have already left, and nobody has started returning just yet."
    "道路は今、人々に見捨てられたように閑散としている。学校から出てきた生徒たちは既に帰ってしまって、今は学校に向かう人間はいない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:464
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_1ecddf6b:

    # "And, with only the school ahead on the road, there doesn't seem to be anyone else around."
    "さらにこの先には学校しかないので周りには誰もいない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:469
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_2aee6244:

    # "The emptiness certainly reflects on Hanako; her arms by her sides each carrying a bag, her head no longer bowed, and back to the upright position…"
    "そんな人の気配のなさは明らかに華子の立ち居振る舞いに反映される。両腕を体の横に伸ばして袋とかばんを持ち、頭はきちんと前を向き、背中はまっすぐに伸びている……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:471
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_4a638b2d:

    # "It's almost as if she were enjoying this walk."
    "まるで散歩を楽しんでいるかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:473
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_4a7474ba:

    # hi "So, why all these weird things? Mixed Spice? Why would you need that in school?"
    hi "で、どうしてそんな変わったものばかり買ったんだ？　スパイスミックス？　そんなの学校で必要か？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:478
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_b172874e:

    # ha "I… sometimes… like to m-make food."
    ha "と……ときどきだけど……料理するのが好きで……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:480
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_7dd42bab:

    # hi "Well, yeah, so do I but… spices?"
    hi "ああ、俺もだよ。だけど……スパイスミックスってどういうことだ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:482
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_09a56195:

    # hi "That's a little more advanced, don't you think?"
    hi "ちょっと上級者向けじゃないのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:487
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_0f82ed62:

    # ha "N-not really."
    ha "そ、そんなことないよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:489
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_02488693:

    # hi "Well, I think it's cool. You'll have to teach me one day."
    hi "ふむ、それはいいな。いつか俺にも教えてよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:494
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_ff70d1cd_1:

    # ha "S-sure."
    ha "う、うん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:496
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_feef7a46:

    # "She doesn't seem all that sure, but pushing the point doesn't seem all that wise."
    "『もちろん』というほどには見えないけど、そこを突っ込むのは賢明ではないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:498
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_c5cf4bff:

    # "At the very least, she seems a great deal happier than she did on the walk down here."
    "控えめに言っても、華子は道を下って来たときに比べるととても楽しそうに見える。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:500
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_19c6c214:

    # "That alone makes me a little happier."
    "それだけで俺も少し楽しくなる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:508
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_03fd12ef:

    # "Outside the girls' dorm, Hanako and I sort out the grocery bags with our respective purchases."
    "女子寮の前で、華子と俺はコンビニの袋を各々が買った品物ごとに分類する。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:510
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_dfcad5a0:

    # "In comparison, my things look positively plain."
    "並べてみると俺の買ったものがとても地味に見える。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:512
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_226c4572:

    # hi "I tell you, you're putting me to shame here…"
    hi "なんだかさ、俺が買ったものが普通すぎて恥ずかしくなってくるな……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:517
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_e199c186:

    # ha "N-no I'm not… I just…"
    ha "ち、ちがうよ……私はただ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:519
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_057626e7:

    # hi "I'm only joking."
    hi "冗談だって"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:524
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_04ccf85e:

    # hi "I have a stack of homework that I skipped last week, so I must leave now."
    hi "先週休んじゃったから宿題が溜まってるんだよね。だから今日は帰らないと"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:526
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_22199bc7:

    # hi "Will you be all right getting that to your room?"
    hi "部屋まで運べる？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:531
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_3959e7b8:

    # ha "Y-yeah."
    ha "う、うん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:533
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_5a69b387:

    # hi "Sure? Okay then. I'll see you tomorrow."
    hi "そうか？　わかった、じゃあまた明日な"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:538
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_78c8f662:

    # ha "B-bye."
    ha "じゃ、じゃあ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:545
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_5ef52fb6:

    # "We part ways, and I return to my room."
    "華子と別れ、俺は自分の部屋へと戻る。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:550
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_47418ef9:

    # "Piles of papers sit upon my desk, begging to be completed. With the entire ruckus of the last week, I've barely had any time to catch up."
    "宿題の紙の山が机の上で『早く終わらせてくれ』と俺に語りかけてくる。先週の騒ぎのおかげでほとんどやる暇がなかった。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:552
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_3b4cf5ec:

    # "I tried to keep up with my studies while I was in the hospital, but some of this stuff I've never seen before, even back in my old school."
    "俺は入院していたあいだの勉強の遅れを取り戻そうとしたけど、その課題には前に通っていた学校でも一度も見たこともないものがある。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:554
translate jp a2_hanako_to_town_to_town_3ea7e3fc:

    # "Totally unprepared, I pop the top on a can of drink, and get to work."
    "俺は完全に見切り発車状態で、缶ジュースのフタを開け作業に取りかかる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:572
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_d79de2cd:

    # "The days are really starting to heat up."
    "この所本当に暑くなり始めている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:574
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_fe194ba3:

    # "This morning, I awoke covered in sweat."
    "今朝目が覚めると、俺の体は汗にまみれていた。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:576
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_802d36a2:

    # "By the time the student body starts leaving their dorms for breakfast and morning duties, the sun has taken full effect; oddly, that puts me in high spirits."
    "生徒たちが朝食と朝の日課を済ませに寮を出るころには太陽はパワー全開になってしまうけど、おかしなことに、それが俺のやる気を奮い立たせる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:578
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_74bcb9ff:

    # "It's not even eight, yet I feel that this day is going to be one of those pleasant, tranquil, warm ones."
    "まだ８時にもなっていないのに、もう今日が静かで暖かく心地よい一日になるだろうと感じる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:580
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_8ea58980:

    # "If I weren't at a school that considered every absence from class as a sign of a life-threatening situation, I'd consider skipping the whole day and just relaxing in the school gardens."
    "『授業を休むこと＝生命の危機に瀕しているサイン』と受け取られる学校に通っていなかったら、全部サボって一日中校庭でくつろいでいるところなんだけど。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:582
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_e38c3d07:

    # "Yes, today will be a genuinely lazy day."
    "ああ、今日は本当にのんびりとした一日になりそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:584
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_7464266b:

    # "For a second, I stop in mid-stretch, and consider the nurse's warning about exercise. Maybe I should have kept up those morning jogs."
    "俺は少しのあいだ途中で動きを止め、ナースに運動について注意されていたことを思い出す。朝のランニング、続けるべきだったかもしれないな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:586
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_28d35147:

    # "Running with someone like Emi might have been a little testing, but if I worked at my own pace…"
    "笑美みたいな子と一緒に走るのはちょっときつかったかもしれないけど、もし俺が自分のペースで走っていたら……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:588
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_2b77d856:

    # "Ah, who am I kidding? I couldn't stick to something like that without some kind of motivation."
    "いやいや、何言ってるんだ。なんのモチベーションもないのに、そんなのやり通せるわけがないだろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:590
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_9fd9121e:

    # "It's not like I sit around all day. The walk to and from the convenience store counts as exercise, right? Especially the walk back up the hill…"
    "俺だって一日中座っているわけじゃない。コンビニまで行き来するのだって運動のうちだよな？　特にこの高台まで登って帰ってくるときとか……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:592
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_58cd49dc:

    # "Yeah, it's no big deal. Compared to months lying in a hospital bed I'm getting plenty exercise."
    "うん。気にしないでもいいさ。何か月も病院のベッドで寝ていたのと比べれば、俺は豊富な運動をしているし。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:597
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_7d07848a:

    # "It seems that I'm not alone in my appreciation of the day."
    "さっき俺が今日という日へ下した評価は、どうやら自分だけが思っているわけではないようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:599
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_0e426bd5:

    # "Nearly every member of the class is glancing through the window and into the tantalizing sky."
    "クラスのほぼ全員が窓の外の誘うような空を眺めている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:601
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_b9d5d43e:

    # "Even the steadfast Shizune seems to lack her usual vigor for schoolwork."
    "しっかりものの静音でさえ、いつも勉強に向けている熱心さを失っているようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:603
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_39535cf4:

    # "Misha, as brazen as ever, has even unbuttoned the top buttons of her shirt and is fanning herself with a note book."
    "相変わらずあつかましいミーシャはシャツの第一ボタンさえも外してしまい、ノートであおいでいる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:605
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_f1c4b14d:

    # "I must have been staring, as she's now sticking her tongue out at me."
    "俺はミーシャをジロジロ見ていたに違いない。それに気がついたミーシャがこちらを向いて舌を出している。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:607
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_f5ccf72c:

    # "However, she shows no signs of halting her efforts, nor is she trying to hide the fact."
    "だけどその行為を止める素振りは見せないし、その事実を隠そうともしない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:611
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_750865fe:

    # "The lunch bells seem to catch everyone by surprise, and the class empties at a much slower pace than usual."
    "昼休みの開始を告げる鐘にみんな驚いたようだ。そしていつもに比べてとてもゆっくりと人が、はけていく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:613
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_d7a6c350:

    # "The heat seems to be draining the need to rush from everyone."
    "この暑さがみんなから急ぐ必要性を吸い取っているようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:617
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_157892b3:

    # "Well, almost everyone."
    "まあ、そうでもない人もいるけど。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:622
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_eae2a53e:

    # ha "H… Hisao?"
    ha "ひ……久夫くん？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:624
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_3a260c25:

    # hi "Hey there Hanako, what can I do for you today?"
    hi "やあ華子、今日はどうしたの？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:626
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_91d2ef49:

    # "Hanako already has a lunch bag in hand."
    "華子はもう弁当袋を手に持っている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:628
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_c4d155c9:

    # "I don't have to be a detective to work out where this is going."
    "探偵にならなくたって、これがどういうことかはわかる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:633
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_fdad5312:

    # ha "Um… would you like to have lunch with us again?"
    ha "あの……もしよければ、またお昼ご飯一緒に食べない？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:638
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_56c24a4b:

    # ha "I… I brought enough for everyone…"
    ha "み……みんなの分……持ってきたから……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:640
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_b1520968:

    # hi "Awesome. You don't have to be so stiff about it though."
    hi "おお、すごいな。でもそんなに緊張する必要ないからな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:645
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_63539c2e:

    # ha "Ah… right."
    ha "あ……うん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:647
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_d1e8fa95:

    # hi "I take it we're going to the tea room?"
    hi "あの紅茶の部屋に行くってことでいいのかな？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:652
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_913ee39d:

    # ha "P… please."
    ha "そ……それでよければ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:657
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_32770c6a:

    # ha "Lilly said she'll meet us in there, so we should… should…"
    ha "リリーはそこで落ち合おうって言ってたから、その……い……一緒に……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:659
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_b0b0ea97:

    # hi "Should?"
    hi "一緒に？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:664
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_e363999a:

    # ha "…should go ahead together…"
    ha "…………一緒に行ったほうがいいんじゃないかな……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:666
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_f8846f9d:

    # hi "Sounds like a plan. This heat has made me pretty hungry."
    hi "うん、それがいい。この暑さでかなり腹が減ってるんだよね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:668
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_1e6b4ddd:

    # "Hanako breathes a sigh of relief, and I gather my things together."
    "華子は安堵の息をつき、俺は勉強道具をまとめる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:675
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_e079fafe:

    # "As usual, the aura of the tea room is refreshing, feeling isolated from the rest of the world."
    "いつものように紅茶部屋の雰囲気はさわやかで、他の世界から隔離されているように感じる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:677
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_1d3c58cb:

    # "Then again, the usual din of the school seems to be a bit subdued; most likely from laziness promoted by heat exhaustion."
    "だけど今日はいつもより校内が少し静かな気がする。おおかた、この暑さからくる疲れで引き起こされている倦怠感のせいだろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:679
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_cc23e121:

    # "Hanako slowly spreads her food on the table, intently focusing on every little movement, as if she's trying to keep her mind off other thoughts."
    "華子はまるで雑念を振り払うかのように、小さな動き全てに一心不乱に集中しながら、ゆっくりと昼食をテーブルに広げる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:681
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_10b8774d:

    # "It's not much, but I can tell from her demeanor that she has prepared everything with utmost care."
    "大したことじゃないけど、そんな彼女の振る舞いから華子はこの上ない注意を払って全ての準備をしたのだと感じられる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:683
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_54723c24:

    # hi "I guess Lilly isn't here yet. Should we start without her?"
    hi "リリーはまだ来ないみたいだな。先に俺たち二人で始めたほうがいいかな？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:690
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_8ad775e7:

    # ha "S-she'll be here soon…"
    ha "す、すぐ来るよ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:695
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_ad3f78d5:

    # "Hanako struggles with the lid of the container of rice."
    "華子はご飯が入った入れ物のフタと格闘している。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:697
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_fdd97525:

    # hi "Here, let me help with that…"
    hi "ほら、貸してみて……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:699
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_a714ccbd:

    # "I take the container from Hanako's hands, and try to force open the lid."
    "俺は華子の手からその入れ物を受け取ると、フタを開けようと力を入れてみる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:701
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_a207837a:

    # "Try as I might, it seems wedged shut."
    "いくらやっても、フタは金具で留められているかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:703
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_7bb3d935:

    # hi "Let me guess, did you put this in while the rice was still hot?"
    hi "あのさ、ご飯がまだ熱いうちにフタを閉めなかった？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:708
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_d5c541be:

    # ha "Y-yes. I was in a rush…"
    ha "う、うん。急いでて……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:710
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_0b68056b:

    # "I put the container on the table between us."
    "俺は二人で挟んだテーブルに入れ物を置く。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:712
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_ea9d6eb8:

    # hi "I thought so. It looks like this is wedged shut. We'll need some hot water to get it open."
    hi "だと思ったよ。金具で留まってるみたいにぴったり閉まってる。開けるには熱いお湯がいるね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:714
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_04877fa6:

    # hi "But that could be a pain in here. We'd get water everywhere."
    hi "でもここじゃ大変そうだな。水ならどこでも手に入るけど"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:716
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_262dc552:

    # li "Well, in that case, how about I contribute to today's meal?"
    li "なるほど。では、本日のお昼ご飯に私が貢献するというのはいかがでしょうか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:728
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_fdcddff6:

    # "At the door, Lilly smiles while holding up a bag stocked with various buns and bread rolls. I can't help but do the same."
    "ドアのところでリリーが色々なパンが入った袋を手にぶら下げて微笑んでいる。俺もつられてつい微笑みかえしてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:733
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_404768e6:

    # li "Since you two had a change of plans because of me, I thought I would bring a little something."
    li "先日は私のせいでお二人の予定が狂ってしまったので、なにか持っていこうと思っていたんですよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:735
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_c7d1e465:

    # hi "Thanks, Lilly. Here, let me get that for you…"
    hi "ありがとう、リリー。ほら、それ俺が持つよ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:741
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_e986c8d0:

    # "With a little guidance, Lilly's bread assortment joins Hanako's rice-less platter. I hastily make some tea to complete the picture."
    "少しの手助けとともに、リリーが持ってきた様々なパンが、華子のご飯抜きの昼食盛り合わせに加わる。俺はこの光景を完成させるために急いで紅茶を入れる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:743
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_a6d37fd9:

    # hi "Well, I'm looking forward to this."
    hi "よし、これを楽しみにしていたんだよね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:748
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_a56ec980:

    # "As I take a bite, I notice Hanako trying her hardest to not look like she is looking at me."
    "一口目を口にしたとき、華子が俺を注視している素振りを見せないように、懸命の努力をしていることに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:750
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_4ad1cd68:

    # "It's nothing special, but then again I can't really complain. I'm pretty lazy when it comes to cooking for myself."
    "特別おいしいってわけじゃないけど、考えてみると文句を言うことはできない。自炊するとなると、俺はかなり無精だからな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:752
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_305b12e5:

    # hi "Not bad, I guess this is made with the stuff you bought yesterday?"
    hi "悪くないな、昨日買った材料で作ったのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:757
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_13b7ab07:

    # ha "Y-yes."
    ha "は、はい"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:759
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_d68dd63c:

    # "Hanako's eyes shout at me, begging for some kind of feedback."
    "華子の目が感想を求めてこちらを凝視する。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:761
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_df4640b6:

    # hi "Well it was clearly worth it. Thanks, Hanako."
    hi "うん、それだけの価値はあったな。ありがとう、華子"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:766
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_f67761ee:

    # ha "I… I wanted to show you this… after yesterday…"
    ha "あ……これを見せたかったの……昨日話してたから……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:768
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_26851b0f:

    # hi "It's okay. I was just a little surprised at the stuff you were buying."
    hi "大丈夫だよ。華子が買った材料にちょっと驚いただけだから"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:773
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_1473ba3b:

    # li "Hanako's always liked to experiment when it comes to food. I think it's good… most… of the time."
    li "華ちゃんは食べ物のことになるといつも実験したがるんです。大概は……良い結果だと思いますよ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:775
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_e47b5ede:

    # "While Lilly's smile doesn't waver, the slight change in her tone tells me that things have not gone so well in the past."
    "リリーは笑顔を崩さないけど、わずかな声色の変化から、過去には芳しくない結果もあったことが伝わってくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:777
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_ee3b6710:

    # "And it's not like Hanako has many people to sample her cooking…"
    "それに、華子の料理を試食するような人がそうそういるわけでもないし……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:781
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_2dbc629a:

    # "Hang on… was Lilly waiting for me to go first? She didn't start eating until after I said it was all right…"
    "待てよ……リリーは俺が最初に食べるのを待ってたんじゃないか？　俺が大丈夫と言うまで食べなかったよな……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:783
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_aebaf96f:

    # "Her cheeky grin tells me that this was a deliberate action on her part. I'll have to try and work out how to get one over her in the future, to make up for this."
    "リリーの小生意気な笑いを見てこれが彼女による計画的犯行だったことがわかる。いつか今日の仕返しに、どうにかして一本取ってやらなきゃならないな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:785
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_14edd9ad:

    # hi "Well, it's good, and that's all that counts, right?"
    hi "まあ、おいしかったし。それが一番大事だよな？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:790
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_40ca9b49:

    # ha "R-right."
    ha "そ、そうだね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:795
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_6d42d438:

    # "Lilly, satisfied at not being the first to sample Hanako's creation, begins to consume the food in front of her."
    "リリーは華子の『創作』の最初の毒味役にならずに済んだことに満足して、目の前の食事を食べ始める。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:797
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_959dd891:

    # "I find myself staring as I watch her chopsticks gently touch the plate, their tips delicately poking and tracing to quickly ascertain the positions of the food as she dexterously picks it up."
    "リリーは器用に食べ物を箸で持ち上げるとき、箸をそっと皿に当て、先端で慎重につついたりなぞったりして、素早く食べ物の位置を把握している。俺はその様子に知らず目を奪われていることに気づく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:799
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_2e53826d:

    # "One might think she were a child playing with her food if not for the situation, though she does it with such care and thoughtlessness that it's obvious this is simply how she eats this kind of meal."
    "こんな状況でなければ、リリーは食べ物を弄ぶ子供と思われていただろう。ただこれだけ慎重に、そして無頓着に行っているのを見れば、普段からこういう食べ方だというのは明らかだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:801
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_5dbf722b:

    # "Not wanting to miss out, I start filling up myself."
    "機会を逃す前に俺も空腹を満たす作業に入る。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:806
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_94829a7c:

    # "Hanako takes a different approach, waiting until Lilly and I have our hands clear before quickly snatching up her share."
    "華子は俺たちとはまた違うアプローチを取る。リリーと俺が手をどけるのを見計らって、素早く自分の分を取り分ける。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:813
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_b72570f2:

    # "Before long the containers are empty, save for the still-shut rice container."
    "間もなく入れ物は空になる。……閉じたままのご飯のケースを除いて。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:818
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_59b45e71:

    # li "Thank you Hanako, that was filling."
    li "ありがとう、華ちゃん。お腹いっぱいです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:823
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_6dde9eb9:

    # ha "N-no… thank you for the bread…"
    ha "こ、こっちこそ……パンありがと……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:825
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_b68f1c55:

    # hi "Yes, it would have been a disaster if not for that."
    hi "うん、あれがなかったらひどいことになってただろうしね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:830
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_d1a80f84:

    # li "You're both welcome."
    li "どういたしまして"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:835
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_d05c3672:

    # li "But now, I must be getting back. It's far too easy to be late after eating here."
    li "でも私はもう戻らなくてはならないんです。ここで食事をした後はとても遅刻しやすいんですよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:837
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_f7569242:

    # hi "Yeah, I see what you mean. I think we'll just clean up here and then head off."
    hi "ああ、言いたいことはよくわかるよ。俺たちは片付けてから戻るよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:842
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_2db9ae35:

    # li "Well then, good day."
    li "では、ごきげんよう"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:853
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_91f65439:

    # "Lilly leaves, her cane tapping away down the quiet hallway."
    "リリーが去っていき、彼女の杖が床を叩く音が静かな廊下を下っていく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:855
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_12f6d2bc:

    # "Hanako and I quickly pack our things and stay seated, waiting for the bell."
    "華子と俺は素早く片付けをすると腰を下ろして鐘が鳴るのを待つ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:864
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_5de14c10:

    # "Together, we stare out the window and into the endless azure sky."
    "俺たちは二人で窓の外の終わりなき紺碧の空を見つめる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:868
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_4b942b3a:

    # "If it weren't for the pealing of the bells, I would have sworn that time had stopped."
    "もし鐘が鳴らなかったら、時が止まったと断言するんだけどなあ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:870
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_1ad2c5e5:

    # "The urge to skip class rises in my gut."
    "次の授業をサボってしまえという衝動が俺の本能から湧き上がる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:872
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_7d7d9118:

    # "I shoot a glance at Hanako, who shows no signs of moving either."
    "俺と同様、動く素振りを見せない華子に視線を飛ばす。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:874
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_450101e2:

    # ha "Not… just yet…"
    ha "まだ、もう少しだけ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:884
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_b55f1ccc:

    # "The interval between the warning bells and the end of lunch bells passes in the blink of an eye."
    "昼休みの終わりを告げる鐘と予鈴のあいだの時間は瞬く間に過ぎる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:886
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_6a91e7ab:

    # hi "We really should go… people will freak out and start a search party if we skip…"
    hi "もう行かないと……もし俺たちがサボったらみんなおかしな想像して、捜索が始まるぞ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:891
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_82710fcb:

    # "Hanako sighs."
    "華子がため息をつく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:896
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_e3554cc0:

    # ha "You're right."
    ha "そうだね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:901
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_56dbcd7d:

    # "Slowly, she rises to her feet, and I follow suit."
    "華子がゆっくりと立ち上がり、俺も後に続く。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:906
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_ee16115e:

    # "Silently, we make our way up the old stairs to the third floor and then to our classroom."
    "俺たちは無言で３階へ続く古い階段を上り、自分たちの教室に向かう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:913
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_c74e1be1:

    # "At the door, I take point and open the door ahead of Hanako, bowing my head down in apology in advance."
    "ドアの前で俺は先頭に立って、先手を打って謝るためにあらかじめ頭を下げたまま、華子よりも先にドアを開ける。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:920
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_a5ce169e:

    # hi "I'm sorry we're late, teacher."
    hi "遅れてすいません、先生"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:924
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_8a946aea:

    # "I am greeted not by stern words, nor by an angered instruction to take my seat, but simply by the silence created by fifteen or so students trying not to laugh."
    "俺は厳しい言葉でも、席に着けという怒った命令でもなく、ただの静寂に出迎えられる。１５人ほどの生徒が笑いをこらえている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:926
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_ab711778:

    # "Mutou, ever tardy, has yet to arrive. However, the fact that Hanako and I have arrived together is blatantly obvious."
    "武藤先生はいつもの例に漏れずまだ来ていない。しかし華子と俺が一緒に教室に戻ってきたという事実は揺るがない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:931
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_9766aa67:

    # mi "Pff… pffwa…"
    mi "プククッ……プフファ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:933
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_456a618c:

    # "Make that about fourteen students trying, and one student failing."
    "訂正。こらえてるのは１４人くらいで、１人はこらえきれてない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:940
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_99545ec2:

    # mi "Pft-bwahahaha! The lovers return~!"
    mi "ぷふっ……ぶぁっははは！　カップルのおかえりで～す！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:945
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_097f05a0:

    # mi "WAHAHAHA~!"
    mi "わははは～"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:947
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_5a3a6a91:

    # hi "Yeah, thanks. You can calm down now."
    hi "どーも。そろそろ落ち着けよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:960
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_a7fb9029:

    # "I step through the door, and realize that Hanako is firmly pressed against my back, hiding herself from the class."
    "俺はドアをくぐったところで、華子がクラスの連中から身を隠すように俺の背中にぴったりとくっついているのに気がつく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:969
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_9e63a96e:

    # "With my steps coming closer to my desk, she eventually breaks from me and stiffly walks to her own. Her efforts to mentally block everyone's presence from her mind are written fairly clearly on her face."
    "俺が自分の机に近づくと華子は俺から離れてぎこちなく自分の席へと歩いていく。彼女の顔には、みんなの存在を自分の心から精神的に遮断しようという努力がはっきりくっきり書かれている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:974
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_533e7eeb:

    # "Quickly checking the door for any signs of the teacher's arrival, I make a trip to Hanako's desk and whisper in her ear."
    "先生が来ないかサッと確認してから、俺は華子の机まで行き、耳元でささやく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:976
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_e4de6562:

    # hi "Don't worry about Misha, she's always like this. I enjoyed myself today. Don't sweat it, okay?"
    hi "ミーシャのことは気にしないでいいから。あいつはいつもこんな感じだし。今日は楽しかった。心配するなよ、オーケー？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:978
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_6fd4fef2:

    # "Hanako nods her head behind her folded arms, but still doesn't show her face."
    "華子は抱え込んだ腕の中でうなずくけど顔は見せない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:992
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_e86aca05:

    # "I yearn to stay and console her more, but Mutou picks this exact moment to enter the class, halfway through his lecture, as if he started it in the hallway."
    "俺はもう少しここで華子を慰めていたいんだけど、タイミング悪く武藤先生が教室に入ってきてしまう。廊下から授業を始めたかのように、既に話半ばだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:997
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_5d2876e1:

    # mu "…which, of course, is directly proportional to the charge but inversely proportionally to the square of the distance…"
    mu "……もちろんこれは電荷に比例するが距離の２乗に反比例しており……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1004
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_6d868831:

    # "He's so engrossed in his speech that he doesn't even notice me sneaking back into my seat from Hanako's desk."
    "先生は俺が華子の机から自分の席までこっそり戻っているのにも気づかないほど熱心にしゃべっている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1006
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_01944858:

    # "While Mutou's spiel rambles on, Misha leans over to me."
    "武藤先生のとりとめもない話が続くなか、ミーシャがこちらへ体を傾けてくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1018
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_f21fa221:

    # mi "The teacher may not have noticed your tardiness, but I did."
    mi "先生はひっちゃんの遅刻に気づいていないかもしれないけど、わたしはそうはいかないよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1020
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_346b6496:

    # "That much is obvious from the show you just put on."
    "さっきの一幕を見ればそんなことはわかるっての。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1025
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_671bcaf7:

    # mi "I have been instructed to let you off the hook for today, but only on one condition."
    mi "今日はひっちゃんを助けてあげるように言われてるんだけどね、一つだけ条件があるの"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1027
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_52b091f1:

    # hi "Oh? And what would that be?"
    hi "ええ？　なんだよ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1032
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_a4a172ca:

    # mi "You have to help us this afternoon~!"
    mi "今日の午後はわたしたちの手伝いをすること～！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1034
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_922e8834:

    # "I crane my neck to look over Misha's shoulder."
    "俺はミーシャの肩越しから向こうを見るために首を伸ばす。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1036
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_0a4b77bd:

    # "Shizune is conveniently not making eye contact with me."
    "都合よく静音はこちらを見ていない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1038
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_aa78da23:

    # hi "Fine. Just for today."
    hi "わかった、今日だけだぞ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1040
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_ae1dd96c:

    # hi "I've already told you I'm not joining the council, remember?"
    hi "生徒会には入らないって前に言ったからな、覚えてるだろ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1045
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_80420c9b:

    # mi "Of course! Doing so could be considered… um, considered…"
    mi "もちろん！　それじゃあ……それじゃあ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1050
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_96f58dc2:

    # "She looks down at her notebook, obviously looking for her place in her script."
    "ミーシャはノートに目を落とす。明らかにそこに書いてあるものの中から次にどう返したらいいのかを探している。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1055
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_6979903f:

    # mi "…under duress and hence would be against regulations."
    mi "……それじゃあ脅迫だもんね、法律違反になっちゃうよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1057
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_0a5b7502:

    # hi "How very strange of you to be considerate of the regulations now."
    hi "今更法律を気にするなんて、お前らしくないな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1062
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_d5ecf66d:

    # mi "Things should be done by the book!"
    mi "物事はルールに従ってやらなきゃだめなの！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1067
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_921d7f42:

    # mi "It's just that the book hasn't been written for every situation, so there are times when it can be ignored."
    mi "ただ、全ての状況に合わせてルールが書かれてるわけじゃないの。だから無視していいときもあるんだよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1069
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_b444b045:

    # hi "And yet, you two wonder why no one else wants to be in the Student Council…"
    hi "これでお前ら２人とも、みんなが生徒会に入りたがらない理由がわからないっていうんだからな……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1085
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_02e82071:

    # "After poking her tongue out at me, Misha returns to her workbook, and we battle our way through the latter half of the school day."
    "ミーシャは俺に向かって舌を出した後課題に戻り、俺たちは午後の授業を切り抜けるのに悪戦苦闘する。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1099
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_2b074432:

    # "Before I can even stand up, Misha and Shizune have placed their hands on both my shoulders."
    "俺が立ち上がることさえできないうちに、ミーシャと静音がそれぞれの手で俺の両肩を掴んでしまう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1101
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_a71cf44c:

    # hi "Hey, I said I'd help out, damn…"
    hi "おい、手伝うって言ったろ、ったく……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1108
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_b44d2576:

    # mi "This is just insurance, Hisao, insurance~!"
    mi "ひっちゃん、これはただの保険だよ、保険～！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1122
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_f3decb73:

    # ha "H-Hisao?"
    ha "ひ、久夫くん？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1124
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_a65f3f71:

    # "Hanako timidly tries to leave the room by circling around us and I suddenly realize that this may be my one chance to escape."
    "華子が恐る恐る俺たちの周りをまわって教室から出ようとする。これはミーシャたちから逃げるチャンスじゃないかとひらめく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1126
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_1f4e2443:

    # hi "Oh hey Hanako. What's up?"
    hi "ああ、華子。どうかしたか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1131
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1136
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_17c19b5d:

    # mi "Hey, what makes you think you've got time to chat?"
    mi "ちょっと、おしゃべりしてる時間なんてあると思ってるの？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1138
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_8f1a017d:

    # hi "Oh relax, this won't take long… sorry Hanako, you were saying?"
    hi "落ち着けよ、すぐ済むから……ごめん華子、どうしたんだ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1143
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_8fb9f6f8:

    # ha "I… I was going to go to the library, and… and I thought…"
    ha "と……図書室に行こうと思っていたんだけど、その……それで……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1145
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_cbcc77e7:

    # "Hanako's thumbs dance around each other and her eyes flit around the room, looking everywhere but at us."
    "華子は手を組んで親指を互いにくるくる回し、視線は部屋中にチラチラと動いている。だけど俺たちを見ることはない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1150
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_a8d28f1a:

    # mi "Sorry Hanako, but Hisao has to come with us. He's got work to do."
    mi "ごめんねー華子、ひっちゃんはわたしたちと一緒に来ないといけないの。やらなきゃならない仕事があるんだよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1155
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1160
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_4ba21152:

    # mi "Oh! But you can help too if you'd like."
    mi "あ！　でも華子が手伝いたいって言うならそうしてくれていいよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1165
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_a5709550:

    # ha "Um…"
    ha "あう……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1172
translate jp a2_hanako_tea_leaves_aecacf86:

    # mi "So, how about it, Hisao?" nointeract
    mi "ね、これでどう？　ひっちゃん" nointeract

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1189
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_35e835c2:

    # hi "What do you say, Hanako? If we all help it shouldn't take long at all."
    hi "どうだ？　華子。みんなでやればすぐ終わるぞ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1194
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_92611110:

    # "Hanako's fidgeting answers my question before she can even form the words."
    "華子がなにか言う前からそわそわしているのが俺の質問への答えだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1199
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_854c9bd1:

    # ha "I… I really need to go…"
    ha "ほ……本当に行かないといけなくて……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1201
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_11048bf8:

    # "Well, that was to be expected. Looks like it's just me and the council girls again."
    "うむ、予想通りだった。また生徒会女子２人と俺の３人か。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1203
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_ffe75f53:

    # "It's easier to resign myself to another afternoon's work in the small council office."
    "狭い生徒会室で、華子を交えて作業をすることは諦めることにしよう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1205
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_cee49811:

    # hi "I'll catch up with you later, okay?"
    hi "あとで行くからさ、な？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1210
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_57db572d:

    # ha "O-okay."
    ha "う、うん、いいよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1225
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_ce8c911c:

    # mi "Right! Now that the farewells are over, it's work time!"
    mi "よし！　お別れは済んだわね、お仕事おしごと～！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1230
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_88226440:

    # "Misha and Shizune frog-march me to the student council office, never once letting go of my shoulders."
    "ミーシャと静音は俺の肩をずっとつかんだまま、無理やり生徒会室へと連れて行く。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1232
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_683cf824:

    # "I feel a little bad for ditching Hanako like this, but if this is the price of getting Misha off her back, so be it."
    "こんな形で華子を置いていくのは少し悪い気がするけど、これが華子からミーシャを引っぺがすための対価なら、しかたないか。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1237
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_f84fba54:

    # hi "So then, what are we up to today?"
    hi "それで、今日はなにをするんだ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1244
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_655e6ecc:

    # mi "Debrief!"
    mi "ほうこく！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1246
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_44966046:

    # hi "Huh? Isn't that supposed to happen after something?"
    hi "は？　普通は何かしたあとに報告するもんだろ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1251
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_66701b4e:

    # mi "Yup! We have to collate all of the information from the festival so that Shicchan can debrief the teachers."
    mi "うん！　しっちゃんが先生に報告できるように学園祭の情報を全部整理しなきゃいけないんだよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1260
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_90266d02:

    # "Shizune drops a large pile of paperwork on the desk in front of me, and smiles succinctly."
    "静音は俺の前に巨大な書類の山を置いて短く笑う。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1265
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_bce21edc:

    # mi "You need to sort those out into two piles."
    mi "これを２つの山に分類してほしいの"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1270
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_45734771:

    # mi "One for financial stuff, like receipts, one for feedback, one for positive feedback, maybe one for things that look like they could be problems next year, one for problems that probably won't be able to be fixed…"
    mi "１つはお金関係ね、レシートとか。次は意見書。その次は前向きな意見書、それと来年問題になりそうな意見書があったらそれも別にして。あと１つ、改善できそうにない問題点の意見書……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1272
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_50436f3b:

    # hi "That's a few more than two piles…"
    hi "全然２つなんかじゃないじゃないか……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1277
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_779c8f72:

    # mi "Huh? Oh, right. Yeah I thought it would be only two piles. My bad."
    mi "はれ？　あ、そだね。２つだけだと思ってた。ごめんごめん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1279
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_ff669e88:

    # hi "Right. While I'm doing this, what will you two be doing?"
    hi "わかった。で、俺がこれをやってる間、２人はなにしてるんだ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1285
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_90e910ac:

    # mi "Well, we missed lunch because we were collecting all of these reports, so we're going to go get some food!"
    mi "うーん、報告書を回収してたらお昼食べそびれちゃったから、何か食べてくるつもり！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1287
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_03dbca20:

    # "Why didn't you just sort them out while you were collecting them…"
    "なんで回収するついでに分類しなかったんだよ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1289
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_1f73cf9c:

    # "Thankfully my self-defense mechanism kicks in and prevents me from opening my mouth and further worsening my situation."
    "俺の自己防衛機能が作動したおかげで、口を開いてこれ以上事態を悪化させるのを防ぐことができた。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1294
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_dec9bd86:

    # mi "Eh?!"
    mi "んー？！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1299
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_f30488c1:

    # mi "How is that fair?"
    mi "そんなの不公平じゃない？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1304
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1306
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_68872e00:

    # "I was fretting over the unfair distribution of work so much that I didn't notice that Shizune had kept on signing."
    "俺は不平等な作業分担にうんざりしていて、静音がずっと手話を続けていたことに全く気づかなかった。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1308
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_b0720ed0:

    # "If it weren't for Misha's outburst, I probably wouldn't have noticed at all."
    "もしミーシャが思わず漏らした言葉がなければ、たぶん全く気づいていなかっただろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1319
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_b38922dc:

    # "Shizune seems to be delivering a fairly long string of commands to Misha, and none of them look pleasant."
    "静音はミーシャにかなり長々と指示を出しているようだけど、その中に楽しそうなものはなさそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1331
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_7f68a7cb:

    # "Reaching a conclusion, Misha signs briefly back to Shizune, and then sits down at the desk next to me."
    "指示が終わるとミーシャが静音に短く手話を返し、俺の隣にある机に座る。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1344
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_38366f84:

    # "Shizune waves to the both of us before disappearing out the door."
    "静音は俺とミーシャに手を振ってから、ドアの外に消えていく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1346
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_12c3279e:

    # hi "What was all that about?"
    hi "一体なんだったんだ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1351
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_182710b7:

    # mi "Shicchan was worried that you'd get it all wrong unless you were supervised."
    mi "しっちゃんはひっちゃんが監督なしだと作業をまるっきり間違えちゃうんじゃないかって心配だったんだよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1356
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_fd5e98ee:

    # mi "And since she can't tell you how you are messing things up, she's making me stay. Awww… bummer, I wanted to go with Shicchan!"
    mi "で、しっちゃんはひっちゃんにどこが間違ってるって言えないからわたしを残したの。あーあ……もー、わたしもしっちゃんと一緒に行きたかったよー！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1361
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_65a276d7:

    # mi "But she is going to bring us back some food~!"
    mi "でもしっちゃんは食べ物持ってきてくれるって～！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1366
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_1625412e:

    # mi "How good is that!"
    mi "やったね！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1368
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_b3bb0e4d:

    # "Misha's flippancy is out of this world. From down in the dumps to on top of the world over some calories."
    "ミーシャの軽快さはもはやこの世のものとは思えない。食べ物の話題くらいで憂鬱の底から世界のてっぺんまで昇り切ってしまう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1370
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_7aab42f1:

    # "It's hard to imagine how anyone could operate at that level."
    "他の人がこのレベルに達することができるとは思い難い。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1372
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_3965f6a1:

    # hi "Well, it could have been worse."
    hi "ああ、不幸中の幸いだよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1374
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_1ff25175:

    # hi "So what are we supposed to be doing?"
    hi "で、なにすればいいんだっけ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1379
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_b46f70cd:

    # mi "Collation."
    mi "分類"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1381
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_4e649191:

    # hi "I gathered that."
    hi "それはわかったよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1386
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_ca7ccf0f:

    # mi "Well, let's just start making piles. We'll work out what the piles mean later."
    mi "うん、じゃあ書類の分類を始めよっか。分けた書類の山の意味は後から考えるから"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1388
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_b74f9e7d:

    # hi "Right…"
    hi "そうだな……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1393
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_e7ad2a8d:

    # "We start to separate all of the papers into increasingly complex piles."
    "俺たちは書類を次第に込み入ってくるいくつもの山に分け始める。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1395
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_29aa5c51:

    # "At first it's just simple categories; financial, feedback, incident reports…"
    "最初は大きなカテゴリーに分けていく。収支、意見書、事故の報告……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1397
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_d36b8d86:

    # "Then they split apart into the good and bad reports, and further still, until it starts to look like we've just thrown the papers onto the desk."
    "そしてそれらを良い報告と悪い報告に分け、ついには机の上に書類を投げているように見えてくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1399
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_c0c3b426:

    # hi "This is hopeless."
    hi "絶望的だな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1404
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_70951ebf:

    # mi "Huh? Why? We're doing what we were told, right?"
    mi "へ？　なんで？　言われたことはちゃんとやってるよね？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1406
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_33546fbf:

    # hi "Yes, but it looks like we're just making a mess."
    hi "ああ、だけど俺たち散らかしてるようにしか見えないぞ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1411
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_f6ecce50:

    # mi "No, I think we got a lot done. Shicchan will be able to work out the rest from here."
    mi "ううん。たくさんやったと思うよ。これなら、残りはしっちゃんでもできるでしょ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1416
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_f6aae81b:

    # mi "So I think we can stop about here then."
    mi "だから一旦このへんで作業を止めてもいいかな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1418
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_4d8ad7cd:

    # "It's almost as if Misha's common sense left the room with Shizune."
    "ミーシャの中の常識は静音といっしょにこの部屋から出て行ってしまったようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1420
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_85854635:

    # "Still, there's no point in arguing."
    "だけどミーシャの提案に異議を唱える意味なんてこれっぽっちもない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1425
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_80090940:

    # mi "Anyway…"
    mi "とにかく……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1430
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_d046eaa9:

    # mi "What's the deal with you and Hanako?"
    mi "ひっちゃんと華子はどうなってるわけ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1432
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_c4c69de9:

    # hi "Deal?"
    hi "どうって？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1437
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_0b860f1f:

    # mi "You were hanging out with her today, weren't you~?"
    mi "ひっちゃん、今日華子と一緒にいたよね～？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1442
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_d5797188:

    # mi "Have there been any fireworks? Any gossip that you're withholding from me~?"
    mi "何か二人の仲に進展でもあったの？　ひっちゃん、わたしに言ってない噂があるよね～？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1444
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_32028d64:

    # hi "If I told you about my own circumstances, it wouldn’t be gossip, would it?"
    hi "俺が自分の状況をお前に話したら、それはもう噂じゃないだろ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1449
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_146b66f4:

    # mi "I guess not…"
    mi "まあ、たしかに……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1451
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_1fc1c5e6:

    # hi "We're just friends, I guess."
    hi "華子とはただの友達だと思ってるよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1453
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_4e5a7f40:

    # hi "Why are you so interested? I thought you and Shizune didn't like her…"
    hi "なんでそんなに興味があるんだ？　お前と静音は華子のことが好きじゃなかったんじゃ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1458
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_da73ef7b:

    # mi "It's not really like that. You know Shicchan and Lilly don't get along well."
    mi "ほんとはそういうのじゃないんだよ。しっちゃんとリリーの仲が悪いのは知ってるでしょ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1460
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_7caac522:

    # mi "And since you can't really get Hanako away from Lilly, we don't talk to her much."
    mi "そんでもって華子をリリーから引き離すことなんて実際できないから、わたしたちは華子とほとんど話さないんだよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1465
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_0c02231f:

    # mi "But that doesn't mean that I can't be concerned for her."
    mi "でもだからといって、わたしが華子を心配できないというのとは違うんだよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1467
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_b2bc5141:

    # hi "What is there to be concerned about?"
    hi "何の心配だよ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1472
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_0e9584c2:

    # mi "Well, she never hangs out with anyone else, right? It's no good, Hicchan!"
    mi "うーんと、華子は他の人と絶対に付き合わないんだよね？　そんなの良くないよ、ひっちゃん！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1474
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_ceee4967:

    # "If Shizune and Lilly dislike each other because 'their personalities are different' then I hate to think how Misha and Hanako would get along…"
    "もし静音とリリーが『性格の違い』から互いを毛嫌いしているのなら、ミーシャと華子の関係がどうなるかなんて考えたくもない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1479
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_e16987a6:

    # mi "I mean, in one way or the other, we're all in the same boat here, right~?"
    mi "ていうか、どっちみちわたしたちはみんな同じ環境にいるわけじゃない。そうでしょ～？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1481
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_29f171d3:

    # hi "Well, I guess."
    hi "まあ、そうだろうな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1486
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_1550e607:

    # mi "This one time, when she left class halfway through, Shicchan went to the teacher and asked what was going to be done about it."
    mi "前に一度、華子が授業の途中で廊下に出て行っちゃったときに、しっちゃんが先生の所に行って、華子の扱いはどうなるのかって聞いたの"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1491
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_8d5d4975:

    # mi "He said that every student here has special needs, and that Shicchan shouldn't worry herself about it."
    mi "先生は『ここの生徒は皆、それぞれに特別な事情がある。しっちゃんはそういうことを気にかけなくていい』って言ってた"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1496
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_792f768d:

    # mi "Hanako never does any group work; she just runs off."
    mi "華子はまだ一度も共同作業をしたことがないんだよ、そうなると逃げちゃうから"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1498
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_da5ad839:

    # mi "Isn't that enough to be concerned about?"
    mi "これが心配しないでいられる？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1500
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_df3c9971:

    # hi "I guess you're right. She still hardly says a word when we're talking."
    hi "お前の言ってることは正しいと思うよ。俺たちが話してるとき、今でも華子はほとんどしゃべらないし"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1505
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_9c06efd1:

    # mi "Well, that's more than I have been able to do. Shicchan and I both tried when she started, but she got scared and ran off."
    mi "むむむ、わたしはそこまでできなかったよ。初めて出会った時にしっちゃんとわたしも華子と話そうとしたけど、華子、怖がって逃げちゃったんだよね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1507
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_f4412218:

    # "I consider telling Misha that exactly the same thing happened with me, but she seems caught up in thought."
    "俺も最初は同じだったとミーシャに言おうかと思ったけど、どうやら彼女は考えることに夢中なようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1509
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_0ff585fc:

    # "Listening to Misha without Shizune's influence is… interesting."
    "静音の影響がない状態のミーシャと話すのは……面白い。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1514
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_d45bd06d:

    # mi "I think she needs to realize that people here don't care what she looks like, and that she can trust us."
    mi "わたし思うの。華子はここの人たちは見た目なんて気にしないこと、わたしたちを信用していいってことに気づかなきゃだめだって"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1519
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_7fe248ec:

    # mi "If she could, I'd feel a lot better about her."
    mi "もしそれができたら、わたしの華子に対する印象もぐっと良くなるんだけどな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1521
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_373150f5:

    # "I think this is the longest I have watched Misha without seeing her sign."
    "こんなに長い間手話を使っていないミーシャを見るのは初めてだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1523
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_6a997708:

    # "When she's with Shizune, she is constantly waving her hands about, explaining the world to Shizune."
    "静音と一緒にいるとき、まわりの状況を静音に説明するためにミーシャは絶えず手を動かしているからな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1525
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_847c37fc:

    # "That amount of effort probably places a strain even on an agile mind."
    "あれほどの頑張りは、たぶん回転の速い頭でさえその負担になるはずだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1527
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_d70abca6:

    # "And let's face it; Misha isn't the world's brightest spark."
    "そして正直言って、ミーシャは世界一頭がいいわけでもない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1529
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_482f0482:

    # hi "Well, I'll keep an eye on her for you."
    hi "ああ、ミーシャのためにも華子のことを注意して見ていくつもりだよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1531
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_981c405b:

    # hi "But you should probably apologize for earlier. I don't think Hanako is cut out for that kind of joke."
    hi "でも早めに華子に謝っといたほうがいいぞ。華子はその手の冗談には向いてないと思うし"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1536
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_52309b36:

    # mi "Oh? Oh~!"
    mi "え？　あ～！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1541
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_73d6dd20:

    # mi "I didn't even notice. Sorry."
    mi "気づきもしなかったよ。ごめん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1543
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_3bc4f41d:

    # hi "Don't say it to me, just mention it to her."
    hi "その言葉は俺じゃなくて華子に言ってやれよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1548
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_1ced0beb:

    # mi "All right. First thing tomorrow, I'll speak to her."
    mi "そうだね。まずは明日話してみるよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1550
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_c71898a4:

    # hi "Good."
    hi "それがいいよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1555
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_d7bfe8e2:

    # "A cacophony from the door heralds the return of Shizune."
    "ドアから不協和音が響き、静音が戻ってきたことを告げる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1557
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_dd04e09c:

    # "I guess she can't really tell how much noise she is making."
    "今どれだけの雑音を出したか、静音自身は気づいていないんだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1562
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_7835761b:

    # mi "Oh, Shicchan! You're back!"
    mi "あ、しっちゃん！　おかえり！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1575
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_56815d1b:

    # "Shizune appears, completely laden with goods from the convenience store."
    "コンビニの食料品を山ほど持った静音が現れる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1580
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1585
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_61ab1cd7:

    # mi "There was some surplus left from the festival. Since this is officially festival business, I've splurged a little."
    mi "学園祭の予算に余りがあったんだ。これはれっきとした学園祭の仕事なんだから、少しぜいたくさせてもらったの"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1590
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_1851ac7f:

    # mi "Nice idea Shicchan, ten points."
    mi "ナイスアイディアだね。しっちゃん、１０点！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1592
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_78f06e0c:

    # hi "Is that really allowed?"
    hi "本当にいいのかよ？　それ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1597
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_ef2b123c_2:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1602
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_12e1ee83:

    # mi "For someone who refuses to join us, you seem to take an unhealthy interest in the politics of this council."
    mi "生徒会に入ることを嫌がる割には、ひっちゃんは生徒会の政治問題に不健全な興味を持つようね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1608
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_fe99fe77:

    # mi "I shall punish your insolence by rationing your portion of the feast."
    mi "無礼の罰としてひっちゃんの分減らしちゃおうか"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1610
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_16c9516d:

    # hi "Fine, fine, I get it."
    hi "へいへい、わかったわかった"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1617
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_dc0f00ad:

    # "Misha slides the multiple stacks of paper to one side to make room for the avalanche of food Shizune is spreading out."
    "静音が次々とテーブルの上に広げていく大量の食べ物を置く空間を作るために、ミーシャは分けた書類の山を机の一端にまとめる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1619
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_205e4391:

    # "As I watch my hard yet misdirected work become wasted, I realize that it's little wonder why these two need help."
    "俺がやっていたキツい上に見当違いの作業が水泡に帰すのを見て、道理でこの２人が手伝いを必要としているわけだと気づく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1621
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_204fa05a:

    # "The convenience store meal isn't overly tasty, but at the very least it's filling."
    "コンビニの食べ物は特別おいしいってわけではないけど、少なくとも腹は満たされる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1626
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_ef2b123c_3:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1631
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_347d46dd:

    # mi "Thanks for helping today. Most of the time we just make up the reports for the staff."
    mi "今日は手伝ってくれてありがと。ほとんど先生に出す報告書を書いてただけだったね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1636
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_e6bb266f:

    # mi "This year we can at least make up some relevant headings on the debrief."
    mi "今年は少なくとも何件かは報告書にきちんとした表題がつけられるよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1638
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_6459194e:

    # hi "Are you sure this isn't a corrupt organization?"
    hi "これで腐敗組織じゃないって自称してるんだからびっくりだな？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1643
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_12e2d68d:

    # mi "Not at all, not at all. We're by the book. It's not our fault if the book isn't specific enough."
    mi "違うよ、全然違うよ！　わたしたちは規則に従ってる。その規則にあいまいなところがあるのはわたしたちのせいじゃないよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1645
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_487669db:

    # hi "I thought that was the definition of corruption…"
    hi "そういうのが腐敗の定義だと思ったんだけど……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1650
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_b9c451e0:

    # mi "You think too much~!"
    mi "考え過ぎだよ～！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1652
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_3112c944:

    # hi "You know what? You're probably right."
    hi "奇遇だな、俺もそう思うよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1654
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_ffccc655:

    # hi "Anyway, I must be off…"
    hi "とにかく、俺はもう行かないと……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1656
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_3295eace:

    # hi "…that is, if I'm allowed to leave."
    hi "……その、行ってもいいなら"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1661
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_ef2b123c_4:

    # shi "…"
    shi "……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1666
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_379aa510:

    # mi "Your work has been deemed sufficient. You may leave."
    mi "十分な働きだったわ。行ってよろしい"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1668
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_8d59115b:

    # hi "Well, thank you."
    hi "そうか、サンクス"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1670
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_d7f9fe28:

    # hi "You know, if you stressed the 'free meal' side of things over the 'endless workload' side, you'd probably end up with more recruits."
    hi "あのさ、『果てしない仕事』よりも『タダ飯』の方を強調してれば、手伝いに来る人ももっと増えると思うぜ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1680
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_335486cb:

    # mi "You might just have a point."
    mi "それは一理あるかもしれないね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1682
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_7a4cba29:

    # hi "Well, think about it."
    hi "うん、考えてみろよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1684
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_3e9e6a14:

    # hi "And think about what we talked about… you don't have to tell that to Shizune if you don't want."
    hi "それとさっき話したこともさ……別に言いたくないんだったら静音に言わなくたっていいんだから"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1689
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_a44c1641:

    # mi "What? Oh, right. I'll try to see her tomorrow."
    mi "えっ？　あー、そうだった。明日華子と会ってみるよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1694
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_d28e2228:

    # mi "G'night, Hicchan."
    mi "じゃあね、ひっちゃん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1696
translate jp a2_hanako_office_confessional_18a0dcca:

    # hi "Night Misha, Shizune."
    hi "またな、ミーシャ、静音"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1713
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_444a09e5:

    # hi "Hey, Shizune. I know I said I'd help, but I forgot I'd already made plans. Besides, I helped out more than my fair share last week, didn't I?"
    hi "なあ静音。手を貸すって言ったけど、前々からの予定があったのを忘れてたよ。それに先週は俺の役目以上に手伝っただろ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1715
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_7aecd9d3:

    # hi "I promise I'll make it up to you some other time."
    hi "また今度埋め合わせするって約束するからさ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1729
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_35d80ebb:

    # "Shizune and Misha release their grip on me and have a long, deep, and silent conversation."
    "静音とミーシャは手を俺から離し、長く深い、そして無音の会話を交わす。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1734
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_e965de2c:

    # mi "Well, you have a point there. To be honest, we were only going to spend the rest of the budget on cakes."
    mi "まあ、ひっちゃんの言うことにも一理あるね。実は余った予算でケーキ買おうかって思ってたんだ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1739
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_889c04bd:

    # mi "So, if you're not there, it works out better. More cake for us. Wahahaha~!"
    mi "だからひっちゃんがいなければ好都合だね。ケーキたくさん食べれるもん。わははは～！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1752
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_17b98826:

    # "Shizune about-faces and marches out the door, and Misha skips out after her."
    "静音は回れ右するとドアの外へと出て行き、ミーシャもそれに続く。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1754
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_aa9e09d2:

    # hi "Well, that was a lot easier than I thought it was going to be. Last week those two were like bloodhounds. Or prison guards."
    hi "あれ、思ってたよりもずっと簡単だったな。あいつら、先週は警察犬みたいだったのに。それか刑務官って言ったほうがいいか"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1756
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_2a6e78bf:

    # hi "Or maybe prison guards bred from bloodhounds…"
    hi "それとも警察犬の『刑務官種』かもしれないな……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1758
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_e8ab1114:

    # "I can't believe I just thought that, let alone saying it out loud. I think I need to move away from Kenji."
    "自分がそんなことを考えるなんて信じられない。ましてやはっきりと口に出すなんて。健二から離れる必要があるな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1760
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_89423cc5:

    # hi "…Never mind. Anyway, should we go to the library?"
    hi "……忘れてくれ。とにかく、図書室へ行かなきゃならないんだろ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1765
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_ff70d1cd:

    # ha "S-sure."
    ha "う、うん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1773
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_b0b636f6:

    # "Hanako follows me through the still-crowded halls to the library, using me as a shield."
    "華子は図書室へ続くまだ人の多い廊下を、俺の陰に身を隠しながらついてくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1786
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_ac990948:

    # "As soon as we are through the door, Hanako bolts for the counter, where Yuuko is stacking books."
    "ドアをくぐるとすぐに、華子は優子さんが本を積み上げているカウンターへと走っていく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1791
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_e4fdd64f:

    # "Before I can catch up, Hanako has whispered something to her."
    "俺が追いつく前に、華子は何かを優子さんに耳打ちした。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1796
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_bce8c889:

    # yu "Um, you'd find that in non-fiction, but I don't know where, exactly. If you want I can look it up…"
    yu "うーん、それならノンフィクションの棚にあると思うけど、正確にどこにあるかはわからないわ。よかったら調べるけど……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1801
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_22b7fec0:

    # ha "N-never mind."
    ha "だ、大丈夫"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1803
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_228fbb81:

    # hi "Hey Yuuko, what's all this about?"
    hi "やあ優子さん、何の話？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1808
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_1a474a3c:

    # yu "Oh, Hisao… Hanako was just looking for a book on…"
    yu "あっ、中井くん……華子ちゃんが本を探してて……分野は――――"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1813
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_631a96af:

    # ha "N-nothing…"
    ha "な、何でもない……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1815
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_554acfd2:

    # hi "A book on nothing? In the non-fiction section?"
    hi "何でもない本？　ノンフィクション？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1820
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_b85036dd:

    # ha "I… I was just…"
    ha "わ……私はただ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1825
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_8c153558:

    # "I shoot a glance at Yuuko. She looks like she's about to burst from the pressure of keeping Hanako's request secret."
    "優子さんに目をやると、先ほどの華子の頼みを秘密にするということのプレッシャーから今にも逃げ出しそうだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1827
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_a1444200:

    # hi "Yuuko, what did…"
    hi "優子さん、いったい何を……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1832
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_a35342ac:

    # yu "Chess! She's looking for a chess book!"
    yu "チェス！　華子ちゃんはチェスの本を探してるの！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1834
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_d080932a:

    # "I make a mental note to never entrust Yuuko with any important information."
    "優子さんにはどんな重要な情報も決して委ねない、と俺は心にとめる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1839
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_14302e29:

    # ha "Y-Yuuko…"
    ha "ゆ、優子さん……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1844
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_220c1d79:

    # yu "I'm sorry Hanako… it just slipped out…"
    yu "ごめんね、華子ちゃん……口が滑っちゃった……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1846
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_98e346fb:

    # hi "Well, it's not a secret any more. Come on, I'll give you a hand. I should really brush up on my skills, too."
    hi "まあ、これで秘密じゃなくなったな。行こう、手伝うよ。俺も腕を磨くべきだしな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1851
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_c6454212:

    # ha "O… okay."
    ha "わ……わかった"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1860
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_68a2319b:

    # "Yuuko disappears behind the counter in shame as Hanako and I wander into the depths of the non-fiction section."
    "華子と俺はノンフィクションの書架エリアの奥へと歩みを進めると、優子さんは恥ずかしそうにカウンターの裏へと消えていく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1862
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_e96ba036:

    # "I know there is supposed to be a system for categorizing these books, but I don't see how anyone can decipher it without spending half of their life researching it."
    "これらの本を分類するやり方があるということは知ってるけど、自分の半生をその分類法の研究に費やした人でもなければ、それを読み解ける人がいるとは思えない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1864
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_059633e4:

    # "That's probably why all the librarians I know are neurotic."
    "たぶんそれが、俺が知っている司書がみんな神経質であることの理由なんだろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1866
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_562360bb:

    # "Towards the end of the aisle, between a book on card tricks and some book on kid's games, stands a single book bearing the title 'Chess Tactics for Champions'."
    "通路の終わりに向かって並んでる本のなか、手品と子供向けゲームの本のあいだに『チェス王者への戦略』という本がある。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1871
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_30cddeef:

    # "Before I can reach for it, Hanako has the book in her hands, clutching it to her chest."
    "俺が手に取る前に、華子はその本を手に取って、胸に抱えこむ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1873
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_b2a4f0f7:

    # hi "Well, I guess that's yours then. Mind if I borrow it when you're finished?"
    hi "さて、無事に手に入ったな。そうだ、読み終わったら借りてもいいかな？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1878
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_9c6b1660:

    # ha "S-sure. I… I just haven't really played against anyone but L-Lilly before, so I thought…"
    ha "も、もちろん。わ……私今までリリー以外の人と対戦したことなかったから……だからその……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1880
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_40c9f34e:

    # "Damn. It's not like I was trying to beat Hanako deliberately or anything, but she seems to have taken it to heart."
    "やばい、本気で勝ちに行っていたわけではさらさらなかったんだけど、華子はそう受け取ったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1882
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_56d62937:

    # "Then again, at least this means she wants to play me again. That's a plus, right?"
    "でも、これは少なくとも華子は俺ともう一度チェスをやりたいってことだ。それはいいこと……だよな？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1884
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_bc8460eb:

    # hi "Ha, well it's not like I'm a master or anything; I just played a bit before…"
    hi "はは、俺は上級者でもなんでもないぞ。だってほんの少ししかやったことなかったし……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1886
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_31f5d59b:

    # "It occurs to me that I haven't told Hanako about my condition. I falter for a second, deciding to cover my tracks. That is a conversation for another day."
    "華子に俺の境遇を言っていなかったことが頭に浮かぶ。俺は一瞬口ごもり、自分の過去については黙っておくことに決める。それはまた今度にしよう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1888
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_c5b87b56:

    # hi "…before I came here."
    hi "……ここに来るまでは"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1895
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_ad5d9a65:

    # ha "Are… are you all right?"
    ha "だ……大丈夫？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1897
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_3e727585:

    # hi "Yeah, I was just remembering something…"
    hi "ああ、ちょっと思い出したことがあって……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1899
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_d7b2012f:

    # "When I think about it, I shouldn't be afraid to tell Hanako about my condition and my time in the hospital. Judging by her scars, she probably spent a fair amount of time in a hospital bed."
    "考えてみると、俺は華子に入院中の生活とか体の状態について話すことを恐れるべきじゃなかった。華子の傷跡から察するに、たぶんかなりの時間を病院のベッドの上で過ごしたはずだし。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1901
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_4f50a563:

    # "But, for some reason, I can't bring it up. At least not today, and not on short notice."
    "だけど、どういうわけか、言い出すことができない。少なくとも今日はだめだし、突然言うのもなしだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1903
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_87bb079e:

    # "Eager to break off the conversation, I grab a random book from the shelf."
    "この会話を中断したくてたまらず、本棚から適当に本を抜き取る。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1905
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_c71dd0ea:

    # "It's some book on the world's fastest roller coasters…"
    "世界で最速のジェットコースターの本……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1907
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_5a3ae132:

    # "…published in 1982. Well, not very up to date, but it should at least be interesting."
    "……１９８２年出版。うーむ、そんなに新しくないけど、少なくとも面白いはずだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1909
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_44ae7593:

    # hi "Well, we both got books now, should we go sit down?"
    hi "さて、二人とも読む本は決まったし、座らないか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1914
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_605a276e:

    # "Hanako seems to accept my bluff, and we head to the reading nook in the back of the library."
    "華子は俺の虚勢を真に受けてくれたようで、俺たちは図書室の後ろの方にある人目につかない読書コーナーへと足を進める。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1919
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_6ffa268a:

    # "Neither of us says a word; we simply open our books and start reading."
    "二人とも言葉を発さず、ただ本を開き、読書を始める。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1921
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_39a89710:

    # "I try to read my book, but it would seem that in 1982 roller coasters weren't nearly as large as the ones built in the decades since."
    "俺も本を読もうとするけど、その本によると１９８２年のジェットコースターは２０年以上経った今のものに比べると小さいようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1923
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_080cedd7:

    # "Most of the ones listed are made of wood. Something about that doesn't seem safe to me."
    "本に載っているもののほとんどが木製だ。それがどうも俺には安全に見えない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1925
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_c8c332f3:

    # "If I'm going to ride on something potentially dangerous, I want it to be made out of steel, or some kind of space-age alloy that has big words like 'Titanium' and 'Ruthenium'."
    "もし危険かもしれない乗り物に乗るのなら、俺は鋼鉄製か、『チタン』や『ルテニウム』という、小難しい単語が入った最新式の合金製がいい。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1927
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_2fd33234:

    # "I quickly lose interest, and my eyes wander across the reading area to rest on Hanako."
    "俺はすぐに興味を無くすと、読書コーナーの中に視線を漂わせ、華子へと向ける。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1934
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_40108196:

    # "Hanako seems absorbed in her book, flicking back and forth through the pages, as if confirming what she just read."
    "華子は夢中になっているようで、自分がたった今読んだ内容を確認するかのように、前後にペラペラとページをめくっている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1936
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_ef1195ee:

    # "I wonder if that's actually effective, or if she's just overloading herself."
    "あれで本当に効果があるのだろうか？　それとも単に理解が追い付いていないだけなのか。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1938
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_9d0ed266:

    # "She unconsciously brushes her hair from her face, temporarily revealing her scar tissue."
    "華子が無意識に顔から前髪を払う。その瞬間、傷跡の皮膚組織が露わになる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1940
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_799f961a:

    # "I'm still not sure about the protocol here. Is it right to ask her about her scars? Or her past? How long was she in the hospital? Does she still visit the doctor?"
    "俺はまだ山久での礼儀を完璧にわかっているわけじゃない。華子の傷跡について尋ねるのは正しいことなのか？　華子の過去のことは？　入院していた期間は？　まだ医者には行っているのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1942
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_321f234a:

    # "These all seem like the questions that you'd ask someone who just transferred to your school, translated into the local language."
    "どの質問も、転校してきたばかりの生徒にするような質問に見える。しかも方言で。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1944
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_e8b533cb:

    # "But, to date, no one has directly asked me any of them. Well, except Rin, but I don't think I should use her as a guide to proper social behavior."
    "でも、今までそんなことを俺に面と向かって聞いてきた人は一人としていなかった。まあ、琳は除くけど。あいつを正しい人付き合いの手本にするべきだとは思わないし。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1946
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_61faf26e:

    # "For the time being, I'll just keep my mouth shut. If someone wants you to know something, then they'll tell you. Trying to force the issue might drive Hanako back into herself."
    "さしあたりは黙っていよう。もし知ってほしいのなら、誰だって自分から言うだろう。無理やり言わせるようなことをしたら、華子はまた心を閉ざしてしまうかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1952
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_c9548257:

    # yu "Um… sorry to interrupt, but I have to close the library now."
    yu "あのぉ……お邪魔して悪いんだけど、もうここ閉めないといけないのよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1956
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_1020d84c:

    # hi "Already?"
    hi "もうそんな時間？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1958
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_9b0f671d:

    # "I check my watch. Somehow, as I was lost in thought, nearly two hours have passed."
    "俺は時計を確認する。どうやら、俺が思いにふけっている間に２時間近く経ってしまったようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1963
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_289bc7c5:

    # yu "Do you want to check out those books? I can do it on the way out…"
    yu "その本借りてく？　帰る途中に手続きできるけど……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1979
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_d3e20edf:

    # ha "P-please."
    ha "お、お願いします"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1981
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_01d2e274:

    # hi "I'm done. I'll drop this one back on the way through. It wasn't as interesting as I first thought."
    hi "俺はいいです。戻る途中に棚に戻しておきます。最初に思ったよりも面白くなかったんで"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1986
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_7d2666f6:

    # "Hanako marks her place with a slip of paper and stands up. The girls head to the counter and I return my book to what I think is the right shelf."
    "華子は紙をしおりにして本に挟み、立ち上がる。優子さんと華子はカウンターへ向かい、俺は元あったと思う本棚に本を戻す。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1991
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_f1753953:

    # "Yuuko scans Hanako's book with practiced precision, yet still manages to fumble it."
    "優子さんは手慣れた正確さで華子の本をスキャンするけど、それでもまた手を滑らせる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:1996
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_8fb26f12:

    # yu "Oh… there we go. Third time lucky. Since this is a non-fiction book, you can only have it for a week."
    yu "ふぅ……はい、できた。三度目の正直よ。ノンフィクションは１週間しか借りられないからね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2001
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_cf84b514:

    # ha "T-that's okay."
    ha "だ、大丈夫です"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2006
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_824a78b4:

    # "Yuuko shuts down the library's computer and herds us out the door."
    "優子さんは図書室のパソコンをシャットダウンし、俺たちを外に出るように促す。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2012
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_19536bae:

    # yu "Argh! I didn't think it was this late already…!"
    yu "あー！　もうこんなに遅くなってたなんて思わなかった！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2014
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_2e2644cf:

    # hi "But you're the one that told us you had to close…"
    hi "でもさっき自分でもう閉めなきゃって言ってたじゃないですか……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2019
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_d8a6afb8:

    # yu "Yes but, I know but, that was before I looked at the time!"
    yu "そうだけど、わかってたけど、時計は見てなかったの！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2024
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_d1ddae7a:

    # yu "I'll see you later."
    yu "またねっ！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2031
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_dfef6bc2:

    # "Yuuko bolts down the hall, her handbag trailing behind her like an awkward streamer."
    "優子さんはハンドバッグを不格好な吹流しのように後ろにたなびかせながら、廊下を駆けていく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2037
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_a9510b03:

    # hi "I guess all librarians really are neurotic."
    hi "司書ってみんな本当に神経質だよな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2042
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_0aeaefef:

    # ha "Huh?"
    ha "へ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2044
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_3249095e:

    # hi "Ah, never mind. I was just thinking that I've never met a librarian that can organize their time, no matter how good they are with their books."
    hi "あ、いや、何でもない。どんなに本に詳しくても、時間を計画的に使える司書を見たことがないなって思ってただけだよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2049
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_97c4e29b:

    # ha "Oh… I k-know what you mean…"
    ha "うん……い、言いたいことはわかるよ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2051
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_215b5fdb:

    # "Hanako smiles in amusement. It wasn't meant to be a joke, but I must have reminded her of some other librarian… or something…"
    "華子はおかしそうに微笑む。冗談で言ったわけじゃなかったんだけど、別の司書の人か何かを思い出させてしまったみたいだ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2056
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_6da4aa5c:

    # ha "I… I have to get back."
    ha "わ……私、帰らないと"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2058
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_cba86884:

    # hi "Yeah, me too. I didn't realize it was this late. Thanks for letting me hang out with you."
    hi "そうだな、俺もだ。こんなに遅くなってるなんて気がつかなかったよ。付き合わせてくれてありがとう"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2063
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_fc223126:

    # ha "N-no problem."
    ha "き、気にしないで"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2065
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_3c0c25b1:

    # hi "I'm going to my dormitory room now anyway, so do you mind if I tag along?"
    hi "どっちみち俺も寮に帰るから、よければ一緒に行かないか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2070
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_57db572d:

    # ha "O-okay."
    ha "う、うん、いいよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2075
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_db742ec9:

    # "Hanako sets off ahead of me, and I need to jog a little to reach her side."
    "華子は俺の前を歩きだす。俺は小走りして華子の隣に並ぶ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2083
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_615fb524:

    # "We walk through the gardens, eventually arriving in front of the dorm buildings."
    "学校の庭を通って、そのうち寮の前に到着する。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2085
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_9cbd5aef:

    # hi "Man, you walk pretty fast. I used to play in a soccer club, and you manage to outpace me."
    hi "おいおい、歩くの速いな。サッカー部だった俺より早いよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2092
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_b10ce9d3:

    # "I kinda regret saying that. It has less to do with her pace than with the fact that my condition has significantly worsened my fitness."
    "俺は自分の言葉に後悔する。それは華子のペースが速いという以上に、俺の病状が運動能力をかなり悪化させたということだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2094
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_9ca065d7:

    # "Hanako's reaction is odd. I expected an awkward attempt to downplay her walking speed, but she just blushes while looking at her feet and smiling."
    "華子の反応は妙だ。てっきり自らの歩く速さを卑下しようとするいつもの不器用な反応が返ってくるものだと思っていたけど、実際には笑みを浮かべながら足下に視線を落として、ただ顔を赤らめるだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2096
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_eb0bf453:

    # "Silence hangs in the air between us. That happens often around Hanako, but feels slightly different than usual this time. After a few seconds, I try to break the silence."
    "二人の間の空気に沈黙が流れる。華子と一緒にいるとこんなことはよく起きるけど、今回はいつもと少し違うように感じる。数秒後、俺は沈黙を破る。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2098
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_76803acd:

    # hi "Here you go. See you in class tomorrow?"
    hi "さてと、また明日、教室で……かな？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2103
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_ff70d1cd_1:

    # ha "S-sure."
    ha "う、うん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2108
translate jp a2_hanako_chess_and_slides_e23cd0e9:

    # "Hanako waves a short goodbye before pushing her way through the dorm's doors. I stand and look at them for a while, before making my way to my own dormitory room."
    "華子は短く手を振ると寮のドアを押しあけて、中へ入っていく。俺は少しの間、突っ立ってその様子を見送ってから、自室へと足を進める。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2122
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_d60ddb48:

    # "Chirping birds."
    "鳥たちがチュンチュンと鳴いている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2124
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_a2ff3ede:

    # "Normally, this would be a good time to reflect upon the beauty of nature."
    "普通ならば、自然の美しさに思いを馳せるいい機会だろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2126
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_ff95a64f:

    # "But it is 6 AM."
    "でも……今は朝の６時だ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2133
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_0b1b56cb:

    # "Covering my head with the pillow, I slam my face into the mattress, hoping that the impact will send me instantly back to sleep."
    "俺は枕で頭を覆って、衝撃で夢の世界へと戻れたらいいのにと思いながらマットレスに顔面をぶつける。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2135
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_e44a4dce:

    # "Futile."
    "無駄だった。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2137
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_241c2ca6:

    # "I toss and turn, but sleep simply won't return to me."
    "俺は寝返りを打つけれど、眠りはまったくと言っていいほど戻ってくる気配がない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2144
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_5eed0909:

    # "All right nature, you've won. See? I'm getting up now…"
    "自然の欲求には敵わない。お前の勝ちだ。わかるか？　へいへい、今起きますよ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2146
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_e5e3f390:

    # "The lack of sleep weighs my mind down, and there's only one remedy for this; a nice, hearty breakfast."
    "睡眠不足で俺のテンションはダダ下がりだ。うまい朝飯をたくさん食べる、テンションを上げるにはこれしかないな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2154
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_112ff660:

    # "It would be nice to be the first person here."
    "一番乗りに出て行くのもいいだろうな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2156
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_d84a63c1:

    # "To be the first to dig into a piping hot pile of food, to sit wherever I desire…"
    "湯気が上がるようなできたての料理に一番にありつくために、好きな席に座るために……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2158
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_bf8fed3a:

    # "It would have been nice."
    "…………だとよかったんだけどな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2160
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_c0ce7b7d:

    # "But even my exceptionally early start has put me behind the most diligent students."
    "俺が自分の中ではとてつもなく早起きしたのにもかかわらず、いわゆる学校で一番勤勉な生徒たちはもうすでに来てしまっている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2162
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_3a176f34:

    # "I guess there are quite a few people that have early starts here, for one reason or another."
    "あれやこれやの理由で、ここには朝が早い奴がかなりたくさんいるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2164
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_ddf49169:

    # "A group of students in sports clothes huddle around one table, eagerly discussing game plans inbetween inhaling great gulps of food."
    "体操着を着た生徒たちが、テーブルのまわりで時折食べ物を吸い込むようなスピードでパクつきながら、熱心に試合の作戦会議をしている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2166
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_da6bf91e:

    # "Scattered around the hall are a number of bleary-eyed students, probably suffering from the same ailment as myself - noisy birds."
    "広間には寝ぼけ眼の生徒もけっこう見られる。たぶん俺と同じ、そう、あのやかましい鳥どもに苦しんでいるのだろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2168
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_22937685:

    # "And, of course, there are the people that actually enjoy getting up this early, the ones with their bags stuffed with textbooks and completed homework."
    "もちろん、かばんを教科書や終わった宿題やらでいっぱいにして、本当に早起きを楽しんでいる人もいる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2170
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_bbabe8df:

    # "It's hard not to despise people like that, even more so when you're tired yourself."
    "そういう人たちを嫌がるなと言われても、それは無理な注文だ。ましてや疲れてるときは尚更だ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2172
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_bf892ab7:

    # "Picking out a familiar face from the thin crowd, I head towards the nearest table."
    "まばらな人混みの中、知っている顔を探しつつ、俺は一番近くのテーブルに向かう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2174
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_91cee339:

    # "Lilly sits alone, delicately feeling her way around a small plate of eggs with her fork."
    "リリーが一人で座って、卵がのった小さな皿の縁をフォークで上品に確かめている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2176
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_062a62f3:

    # "It's almost a shame to interrupt her and her clockwork movements."
    "その動きは機械のように正確で、声をかけることもはばかられる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2178
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_e28ca64d:

    # "I wonder, is this how a blind person zones out? Simply moving in pre-determined patterns learned over the years, just like how a sighted person would eat while reading a newspaper."
    "目の見えない人が何かに夢中になるとこうなるのだろうか？　長年繰り返して身についた、決まり切った動作をしているだけだ。目の見える人が新聞を読みながら食事をするように。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2180
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_973e7a5f:

    # hi "Good morning, Lilly. I didn't expect you to be here this early."
    hi "おはよう、リリー。こんなに早くからいるとは思わなかったよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2187
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_8fc8ed6e:

    # li "Oh, Hisao, you startled me. I didn't know you took breakfast this early."
    li "あら久夫さん、びっくりしました。こんなに早い時間に朝ごはんを食べていたんですね、知りませんでした"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2189
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_463bfda1:

    # hi "I don't. This is an exception to the rule. I'd greatly prefer to be late to school than early to breakfast."
    hi "いや、今日はたまたまだよ。普段なら朝飯のために早起きするより学校に遅刻する方を全力で選ぶよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2194
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_2cb74284:

    # "Lilly gives a small sigh at my admitted tardiness as I begin eating my food."
    "俺が食事を始めると、リリーは俺が遅刻体質であることを自覚していることに小さなため息をつく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2196
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_b4c173d1:

    # "It doesn't take long for her to lapse back into her previous mindless nibbling."
    "まもなくしてリリーはさっきまでの無意識の食事に戻る。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2198
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_cb84d6cc:

    # "Each short motion lacks energy. I suppose this is similar to letting your eyes wander while performing any ordinary chore."
    "このリリーの一連の動作にはエネルギーが欠けていて、普段の雑務をこなすときに周りをキョロキョロ見回してしまうことに似ているなと感じる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2200
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_982e9ac1:

    # "But after a few repetitions of the find food/eat food cycle, Lilly puts down her fork and dabs her lips with a napkin."
    "しかし、食べ物を見つけては食べ、見つけては食べ、を数回繰り返した後、リリーはフォークを置き、ナプキンで口を拭う。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2208
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_bdc0904d:

    # li "Hisao, do you mind if I ask you a question?"
    li "久夫さん、一つ質問してもいいでしょうか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2210
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_70effd09:

    # "Damn. All I want is a little food and about four hours of sleep. And nobody says 'can I ask you a question' for a simple question."
    "ちくしょう。俺が欲しいのは少しの食事と４時間ほどの睡眠だ。そして残念なことに、簡単な質問をするときに『質問してもいいですか』なんて言う人間は誰一人としていない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2212
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_21ce94c5:

    # hi "Sure."
    hi "だろうな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2217
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_cdb69970:

    # li "Do you think of Hanako as a friend?"
    li "華ちゃんを友達だと思いますか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2219
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_20d7c42c:

    # "Huh, this seems like a leading question."
    "あれ、なんか誘導尋問みたいだぞ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2221
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_6a0a81de:

    # hi "I… guess so. Why do you ask?"
    hi "うん……そうだと思う。なんでそんなことを？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2226
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_fd981080:

    # li "No real reason."
    li "特に意味はないです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2233
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_e6c2f3c7:

    # li "I do have another question though. Why is it that you think of her as a friend?"
    li "ただ、もう一つ質問があります。どうして華ちゃんを友達だと思うんですか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2235
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_cf13f7ad:

    # "This is well above my level. What is she expecting from me?"
    "さっぱりわからない。リリーは俺に何を期待しているんだ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2237
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_92dd9db0:

    # hi "I'm not really sure. I guess it's because she's a little different in the way she deals with people…"
    hi "俺にもよくわからないよ。華子は人との接し方が少し違うからだと思う……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2242
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_246959c2:

    # li "Hmm. Since I've known her, she hasn't really connected with anyone."
    li "……私と出会ってから、華ちゃんは本当に私以外の誰とも、関わりを持っていないんです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2247
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_a4434515:

    # li "She doesn't seem interested in other people, and I think people are a little scared off by her appearance."
    li "華ちゃんは他人に興味がないみたいなんです。それに華ちゃんの見た目をみんな少し怖がっていると思うんです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2249
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_2fd3b41c:

    # hi "Really? I thought that kind of thing was, well, discouraged here. Discriminating and such."
    hi "マジで？　ここではそういうことは、その、しないものだと思ってたよ。差別とかさ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2254
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_33a8db27:

    # li "Hmm, if I were to put it one way…"
    li "うーん、言わせていただけるのなら……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2256
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_20db8d7c:

    # "She furrows her brow in thought, a move which makes me slightly anxious as to what she's plucking from her mind."
    "リリーが考え込んで眉間にしわを作る。それを見て、リリーが何を言い出すのか少し心配になる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2261
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_cdfdc1b1:

    # li "I'd say that you're a little naive."
    li "久夫さんは少しウブなんじゃないかと思いますね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2263
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_4059062f:

    # "Naive? I'd be insulted if not for the slightly cynical grin on her face."
    "ウブ？　リリーの顔にシニカルな微笑が浮かんでいなかったら、俺はこの言葉を侮辱と受け取っただろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2265
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_5715c902:

    # hi "I… see."
    hi "な……なるほど"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2270
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_7c277df3:

    # li "While Yamaku has a stronger sense of community compared to other schools, it's far from being free of conflict."
    li "山久は他の学校に比べて強い共同体意識を持っている反面、人同士の衝突がないとは到底言えないのです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2275
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_6b1c4549:

    # li "Rules cannot remove human nature, after all, only suppress it."
    li "規則は人間の本質までは取り除けません。結局ただ抑え込むだけなんです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2277
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_67796def:

    # "That's something I've noticed, actually."
    "確かにそれは俺も気づいていたことだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2279
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_47643aa8:

    # "Just little things, like how certain people and cliques avoid each other in the hallways. It's no different than my old school, really."
    "それは人や仲間グループが廊下でどうやって他の人とすれ違うかといったような、ほんの小さなことだ。俺がいた学校となにも変わらない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2281
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_773ae041:

    # "Even Lilly and Shizune could be considered bitter rivals, even though they both seem like fairly accepting people."
    "リリーと静音でさえ、一見するとかなり心が広そうだけど、犬猿の仲だと言えるだろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2283
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_b803bd26:

    # "Well, at least the Misha-tinted Shizune does; who knows what actually goes on with her fingers and behind her glasses."
    "まあ、少なくともミーシャを通して見る静音は寛容そうだ。ミーシャは静音の指の動きと眼鏡の向こうの目つきの本当の意味を理解しているからな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2285
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_2714796b:

    # hi "I guess you're right. But when I first came here, everything was a bit of a shock."
    hi "リリーの言っていることは正しいだろうけどさ、俺が初めてここに来たとき、何もかもがちょっとした衝撃だったんだ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2287
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_312fa566:

    # hi "I kept on making mistakes, or at least thinking I was making mistakes. Like when we first met, and I said 'I see' to you."
    hi "俺はずっと間違ったことばかりしてた。そうでなくても、少なくとも自分が間違ったことをしてると思い続けてた。俺たちが初めて会ったとき、君に『見たことあるよ』って言ったみたいにね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2289
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_58145d5f:

    # hi "I didn't know if that was considered rude or anything, so I tried to just put it in the back of my mind. Treating people any differently and that kinda thing."
    hi "俺はそれが失礼なことかどうかわからなかったから、とにかく心の奥にしまっておくことにしたんだ。人を特別扱いするとか、そういうことを"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2291
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_897bb7cf:

    # hi "So I didn't. I told myself that Hanako and you and everyone else was just normal, and I tried to ignore the obvious."
    hi "だから俺は特別扱いしなかった。華子とリリー、それに他のみんなは『普通』なんだって自分に言い聞かせて、わかりきっていることにも気づかないふりをしようとしたんだ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2293
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_682f6b66:

    # hi "I talked to Hanako as if she were any other person, and so we became friends."
    hi "だから俺は華子に他の人と同じように話しかけたし、友達にもなった"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2295
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_2e31660f:

    # hi "At least, that's how I think it happened."
    hi "少なくとも、俺はそういうことだと思ってる"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2297
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_dab58a3f:

    # hi "But you know, I feel guilty just from saying something like that aloud. As if it took extra effort to think of Hanako, or you, or anyone here as normal people. I don't think that's right."
    hi "だけどさ、こういうことを口に出して言うだけで悪い気がするんだ。まるで華子やリリーや他のみんなを『普通』の人間だって考えるために特別な努力が必要だって言ってるみたいで。そんなのおかしいと思う"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2302
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_4e2734f2:

    # li "Hisao, I think you are naive, but I also think that you are a good person. It is perhaps one of your better traits."
    li "久夫さん、やっぱりあなたはウブだと思います。でもあなたはいい人なんだとも思います。たぶんこれは、久夫さんの良いところの一つなんでしょうね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2304
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_84c6a8f8:

    # hi "I… suppose… I can take that as a compliment…"
    hi "そう言ってもらえると……ありがたいけど……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2309
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_00147a71:

    # li "Tell me, are you free tonight?"
    li "お聞きしますが、今夜の予定は空いていますか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2311
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_7197e293:

    # hi "If you don't count homework, then I'm as free as the breeze."
    hi "宿題を除けば、そよ風のように自由の身だよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2316
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_dd8c3158:

    # li "In that case, would you care to join myself and Hanako for tea?"
    li "それでは、私と華ちゃんと３人でお茶でもしませんか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2318
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_9a2e9250:

    # hi "Er, I don't really have that much money at the moment, so going out isn't really…"
    hi "うーん、今そんなにお金持ってなくてさ、店に行くのはちょっと……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2323
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_328f7a1c:

    # li "Oh, I didn't mean going out. Just here, this evening."
    li "あら、学校の外に行くつもりはありませんよ。今夜ここでやるんです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2325
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_8d831ddd:

    # hi "You can access the classrooms in the evening here?"
    hi "この学校は夕方に教室に入れるのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2330
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_f0328798:

    # li "No, that's not what I meant. Hanako and I often use my room for tea parties together. Please feel free to drop by after dusk."
    li "いえ、そうではなくて、華ちゃんと私はよく私の部屋で一緒にお茶会をやるんですよ。夕方になったらぜひいらしてください"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2332
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_2347b5f7:

    # hi "Sure, I see no problem with that. What's your room number?"
    hi "わかった。それは大丈夫だけど、部屋番号は何番？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2337
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_1372d309:

    # li "225; Room 25 on the second floor."
    li "２２５号室、２階の２５号室です"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2339
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_c8e7b156:

    # hi "Okay, sure."
    hi "オッケー、了解"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2344
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_955b32eb:

    # li "Well then, I had best be off. I have class representative duties to attend to, after all."
    li "ではもう行きますね。やらなくてはならない学級委員の仕事があるんですよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2349
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_0640266a:

    # li "Until this evening, Hisao."
    li "また今夜、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2351
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_9cba87c8:

    # hi "Yeah, catch you later."
    hi "ああ、また後でな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2358
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_51634f83:

    # "Hang on… was I just invited to a girl's room after hours? Is that even allowed?"
    "ちょっと待て……俺は放課後に女の子の部屋に招かれたんだよな？　これって大丈夫なのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2360
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_9bdcce00:

    # "There is the curfew here, but I've never heard any rules about visitors in the dorm rooms."
    "ここには門限はあるけど、寮の部屋に誰かを呼ぶことについての規則はまだ聞いたことがないぞ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2362
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_b87d2674:

    # "Even still, this is enough to get my sleep-deprived brain jump-started."
    "それでもなお、このお誘いは睡眠不足の脳を活性化させるには充分すぎる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2364
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_6bab9e2d:

    # "Add that to a lukewarm breakfast and you have one hell of a pick-me-up."
    "ぬるくなった朝食に、とんでもない刺激が加わった。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2369
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_20e9e2f4:

    # "I grudgingly go to class, still a little excited at the prospect of breaking the rules."
    "俺はしぶしぶ教室へ向かうけど、規則を破る可能性に今も少しドキドキしている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2371
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_c7f330e4:

    # "I feel a little like a kid planning to sneak out of his window at night."
    "なんか、子どもが夜に窓から外へ抜け出す計画を立てたときの感じに少し似てるな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2373
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_f668619e:

    # "Well, maybe that's going a little too far, but when you compare an invitation to a party to six or so hours of lectures, I know which one wins."
    "まあそれは少し行き過ぎかもしれないけど、お茶会へのご招待と６時間ほどの授業を比べたとき、どっちがいいものかくらい俺にもわかる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2375
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_e519caf4:

    # "Misha and Shizune do little to relieve my boredom either. For once, they seem determined to actually complete Mutou's assignments."
    "ミーシャと静音はどちらも俺の退屈を紛らわしてはくれない。今日に限って、武藤先生が出した課題をちゃんと終わらせようとしている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2382
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_4aa6f748:

    # "Nevertheless, the day eventually winds to a close."
    "とはいうものの、やがて一日は終わりに向かう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2387
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_2788ddae:

    # "I hurry back to my room to wash up and comb my hair. Thankfully I don't run into Kenji."
    "俺は部屋に急いで戻り、顔を洗って髪をとかす。ありがたいことに健二には出くわさない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2392
translate jp a2_hanako_rise_and_shine_ff586a6c:

    # "Before long I am leaving the boys' dorm."
    "少しして俺は男子寮を後にした。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2403
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_f8ecda95:

    # "I nervously rap on the door marked 225, checking my watch once again."
    "俺は時計をもう一度確認しつつ、恐る恐る『２２５』と書かれたドアをノックする。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2405
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_e3819a87:

    # li "Is that you, Hisao? The door is open, you can come in."
    li "久夫さんですか？　開いていますから、お入りください"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2407
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_25499b30:

    # "Lilly's voice lilts through the door and soothes my nerves."
    "ドアの中から聞こえてくるリリーの陽気な声が、俺の緊張を和らげる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2409
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_4070c4d4:

    # "This is the first time I've been invited to a girl's room after dark."
    "日が暮れてから女の子の部屋に招かれるのは初めてだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2411
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_ec61a358:

    # "Even though I know there is no ulterior motive behind this invitation, it doesn't stop my mind running wild with possibilities."
    "たとえこの招待に隠された意味などないのだとわかっていても、その可能性に俺の心は暴れまわるのをやめない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2413
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_f0877089:

    # "One guy. Two girls. In a dorm room. With a tea set."
    "一人の男。二人の女。寮の部屋。ティーセットと共に。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2415
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_588c2faa:

    # "When I put it like that, it sounds a little dodgy."
    "こう言うとちょっとアブナく聞こえるな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2417
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_8338d8e6:

    # "Giving a small sigh to steady myself, I gingerly put my hand on the handle and open the door, craning my head to see inside."
    "小さく息をついて心を落ち着かせたあと、この上なく慎重にドアノブを回して扉を開け、部屋の中に頭を突っ込む。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2434
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_f9d49294:

    # "The door opens completely and I catch my first glimpse of Lilly's room."
    "ドアが完全に開くと、俺の目に初めて見るリリーの部屋の様子が飛び込んでくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2436
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_6c9ec6b5:

    # "Her furniture looks almost antique, but the bare walls and flat surfaces are barely decorated at all. In the center of the room sits a low table, where I see a small tea set at rest."
    "家具のほとんどがアンティーク風だけど、むきだしの壁と平面は全くと言っていいほど装飾されていない。部屋の中央にローテーブルが鎮座し、小さなティーセットが静かに乗っている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2438
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_23dac982:

    # "It seems that everything in this room has its place, possibly excepting the several piles of books stacked up against the wall."
    "この部屋の中にある全てのものには決まった置き場所があるようだ。例外を言えば壁際に積みあがっているいくつかの本の山くらいか。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2440
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_4d3afb09:

    # "My sense of vision isn't the only one to be stimulated; the faint smell of something can be picked up on the air. Nail polish, perfume, makeup… it's hard to describe in any way other than 'girly'."
    "刺激を受けているのは視覚だけではない。何かはわからないが、ほのかな香りが漂っているのがわかる。マニキュア、香水、化粧品……『女の子の部屋の匂い』という言葉以外では形容し難い。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2442
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_e49ed0d4:

    # "My eyes finish their quick sweep of the room, before returning their position onto the girls."
    "部屋を一通り見渡すと、俺は二人の女の子に目を向ける。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2449
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_a83fb251:

    # "Lilly sits next to the small table, wearing very dark blue pajamas. Dark blue pajamas with shorts that show off plenty of her alluring pale legs."
    "リリーはダークブルーのパジャマを身につけて、先ほどの小さなテーブルの隣に座っている。パジャマの下はショートパンツで、魅力的な白い足をたっぷりと見せつけている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2455
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_8e4dba43:

    # "Opposite her, Hanako sits adorned in a conservative light pink gown."
    "リリーの反対側には、控えめな淡いピンクのガウンを着た華子が座っている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2457
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_f6aaab68:

    # "Her hands are firmly fixed between her legs, her shoulders forward, and her head down, as if trying to hide herself in it."
    "両手は足の間にしっかり固定し、背を丸めてうつむいている。まるでガウンの中に隠れようとしているみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2459
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_389cedc0:

    # "It would be easy for her to do; it looks about two sizes too big for her."
    "ガウンは華子のサイズより二回りほど大きく見えるし、やろうと思えば簡単だろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2461
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_7a2d6326:

    # "Waves of flannel flow from her frame, making her look like a child playing dress-up in her parents' clothes."
    "華子の体の上でフランネルの生地が波打って、子どもが親の服を着て遊んでいるように見える。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2463
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_68cb210b:

    # "She looks up to confirm my identity, and the beginnings of a thin smile creep across her face, before vanishing so fast that I can't be sure they ever were there."
    "華子が俺の存在を確認するために顔を上げ、わずかな笑みを浮かべかけるけど、本当に笑ったのかわからないほどすぐにそれは消えてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2468
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_6ddb36dc:

    # li "There's no point in you standing in the doorway, Hisao."
    li "ドアの前に立っていても仕方ありませんよ、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2482
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_d5e9055e:

    # "I take a step into the room, closing the door behind me."
    "俺は後ろ手でドアを閉めつつ、部屋の中に数歩踏み込む。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2487
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_29bc9ba1:

    # li "My my, I'm afraid this really is a small room for the three of us. Would you like to take a seat?"
    li "あらあら、この部屋、三人だと狭いですね。座りませんか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2489
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_269fba85:

    # "I slowly walk to the table and sit down, trying my hardest not to disturb anything along the way."
    "俺は部屋を荒らさないように最大限の努力をしながらゆっくりとテーブルへと歩みを進め、腰を降ろす。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2491
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_5ad7baeb:

    # "I also can't help but steal a quick glance into Lilly's top as I sit."
    "あと、腰を降ろす時にリリーの上半身をちらりと見ずにはいられない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2493
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_ad1a067a:

    # "To be robbed of sight would be a most terrible fate."
    "視覚を奪われるというのは本当に恐ろしい悲劇だろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2498
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_116bb0b2:

    # li "Well now, how about some tea. Hanako, could you please pour?"
    li "さて、お茶にしましょうか。華ちゃん、注いでもらえますか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2503
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_60ab94be:

    # ha "S… sure. Hi… sao… would…"
    ha "う……うん。ひ……さ……くん、こ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2508
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_99fbe8fb:

    # ha "…would you…"
    ha "……こう……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2513
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_d8d7c5a7:

    # ha "…would you like…"
    ha "……こうちゃ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2515
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_3906f248:

    # hi "I would love some tea. Do you need a hand?"
    hi "もらうよ。手伝おうか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2520
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_1e8c396a:

    # ha "N… no, I'm fine…"
    ha "う……ううん、大丈夫"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2525
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_c4efd2c3:

    # ha "Thank you…"
    ha "ありがとう……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2532
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_7e39b933:

    # "Lilly finds it difficult to resist a smile at her companion's nervousness, something I can't really blame her for."
    "華子の緊張ぶりを見て、リリーが微笑みをこらえきれずにいる。無理もないなと俺も思う。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2537
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_7912c95d:

    # hi "Been a tiring day?"
    hi "今日は疲れる日だったのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2542
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_8c015a3e:

    # ha "Y… yeah."
    ha "う……うん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2547
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_5af4c442:

    # "I relax at my place, opposite of the cabinet."
    "俺はたんすの対面に自分の居場所を確保すると、緊張を解く。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2549
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_d318ed41:

    # "To my left is the blue-clad Lilly and to my right sits the pink Hanako."
    "左に青を纏ったリリーが、そして右側にはピンクの華子が座っている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2559
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_340d6e16:

    # "The tea set on the table looks cute as well as practical; painted red with a floral motif."
    "テーブルの上のティーセットは実用的でありながら、赤に花のモチーフをあしらえたかわいい見た目をしている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2561
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_6ce7a5bc:

    # "It looks odd when contrasted with Lilly's plain but generally sophisticated-looking furniture, which leads me to think that Hanako might have picked it out."
    "それは質素だけど洗練された作りのリリーの家具と比べると奇妙に映る。もしかしたら華子が選んだのかもしれないな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2563
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_24c6cf02:

    # "There is a slight 'ting' when Hanako accidentally clips the teapot on a cup as she is pouring."
    "華子が紅茶を注いでいると、わざとではないんだろうけど、ティーポットがカップにぶつかって『カチャ』という音が聞こえてくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2575
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_f284263d:

    # "She breathes in sharply; she must be really nervous, as it's not the kind of thing anyone would worry about."
    "華子がはっと息をのむ。本当に緊張しているに違いない。そんなに心配することでもないのに。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2580
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_6d723c60:

    # "Hanako quivers at her mistake."
    "自分の不手際に華子はわななく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2585
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_319ec7d0:

    # li "It's okay, Hanako. There's no need to be nervous."
    li "いいのよ、華ちゃん。緊張しなくても大丈夫だから"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2590
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_89e418b1:

    # "Hanako seems to find some confidence in Lilly's reassuringly soft-spoken words and deftly pours the next two cups."
    "リリーの安心感のある柔らかな言葉で華子は少し自信をつけたようで、残る２つのカップに手際よく紅茶を注ぐ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2595
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_1b504d01:

    # ha "Here you are, Hisao… Lilly."
    ha "どうぞ、久夫くん……リリー"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2597
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_62d57335:

    # "Hanako carefully places a cup and saucer in front of Lilly and myself. I could get used to service like this."
    "華子が俺とリリーの前にカップとソーサーを注意深く置く。こんなサービスも悪くないな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2602
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_23ce2f9d:

    # li "Thank you, Hanako."
    li "ありがとう、華ちゃん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2604
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_25f4a6b6:

    # hi "Yeah, thanks."
    hi "ああ、サンキュー"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2609
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_a23af8ea:

    # ha "Y-you're welcome."
    ha "ど、どういたしまして"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2614
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_f98cf146:

    # "Lilly searches for her cup, and upon finding it, sips delicately."
    "リリーは手探りで自分のカップを探し、上品に口をつける。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2616
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_fff5a883:

    # "I do the same. This tea tastes somewhat better than the tea we usually have at school."
    "俺も同じように紅茶を飲む。俺たちがいつも学校で飲んでいるものより、いくらか良い味だ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2618
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_7e6d14a4:

    # hi "This is nice, it's so different from any tea I had before…"
    hi "おいしいな、今までに飲んだ紅茶とはまるで違う……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2624
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_a8a0fc2e:

    # li "Looks like you picked the right one, Hanako."
    li "いいのを選んだみたいですね、華ちゃん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2629
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_dab7c8e6:

    # li "You've done well, even if it was a bold move."
    li "よくやりましたね。大胆だったかも知れませんけど"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2634
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_38f80c6e:

    # "Hanako's smile returns, redoubled."
    "華子の顔に笑顔が二倍になって戻ってくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2636
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_391a6f7e:

    # "Even with her blighted face, her shy smile couldn't be called anything but 'cute'."
    "やけどの跡が残っているにもかかわらず、華子のはにかんだ笑みは『かわいい』以外の言葉で言い表すことができない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2641
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_ff8b709c:

    # ha "I'm glad you like it…"
    ha "気に入ってもらえて嬉しい……な"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2643
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_1d2664be:

    # "Hanako, finally beginning to relax, sips from her cup."
    "華子も緊張がとけたようで、カップから紅茶をすすりはじめる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2648
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2651
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_dd6c1788:

    # n "I think back to my chat with Misha the other day."
    n "先日のミーシャとの会話を思い出してみる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2653
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_5fe1268c:

    # n "Is Hanako's behavior something to be concerned about, or is she just shy?"
    n "華子の振る舞いは心配すべきことなのか、それとも単にシャイなだけか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2655
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_e6c818ac:

    # n "And then there was Lilly earlier this morning."
    n "今度は今朝のリリーとの会話を思い出す。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2657
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_b2b0aa22:

    # n "The concern from both of them seemed to be genuine, and they know the situation better than I."
    n "二人の華子に対する心配は心からのものだと思うし、俺よりも華子を取り巻く状況をよく知っている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2659
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_f893aad3:

    # n "But, really, how could I possibly help?"
    n "でも実際、俺にどんな手助けができるっていうんだ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2661
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_7919f76d:

    # n "I'm no plastic surgeon, so I can't really help her appearance. Nor am I a psychologist who can make her more sociable."
    n "俺は形成外科医じゃないんだから、華子の外見をどうにかするなんて無理だ。華子をもっと社交的にしてやれるような心理学者でもない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2663
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_6b966374:

    # n "So what the hell do Lilly and Misha want me to do?"
    n "じゃあリリーとミーシャは一体全体俺にどうしてほしいって言うんだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2665
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_ca2bdec6:

    # n "It's frustrating. Hanako and I are quickly becoming friends on our own accord, and because of that, it's like everyone wants me to solve all her problems."
    n "考えると心が折れそうになる。華子とはお互いの意思で、それも速いスピードで友達としての仲を深めているし、そのせいでみんな俺に華子の抱えている問題をすべて解決することを望んでくるみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2667
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_06c75d2a:

    # n "And I have no idea how to do that."
    n "で、俺にはどうすればいいか全くわからない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2669
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_55e6685b:

    # n "No one can cure my heart, nor Lilly's eyes, nor anyone who is here, in this school."
    n "この学校の誰も、俺の心臓を治すことはできない、リリーの目も、ここに居る誰のことも。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2671
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_f57eaa86:

    # n "However, I see no harm in becoming better friends with Hanako. Now that she's warming up to me I kind of enjoy hanging out with her."
    n "でも華子と友情を深めていくことは嫌じゃない。今は華子が俺に好意的になってくれているので、俺も華子と一緒に過ごす時間を楽しんでいる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2674
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2679
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2682
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_00bbcaa4:

    # n "{vspace=120}Something about this makes me think about Lilly's question at breakfast."
    n "\n\n\n\nここまで考えて、俺は朝食の時にリリーから投げかけられた質問を思い出す。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2684
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_8e1b1645:

    # n "Why am I friends with Hanako?"
    n "どうして俺は華子の友達なんだろう？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2686
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_268a5761:

    # n "Lilly seems genuinely concerned for Hanako's well being, but it's not like I can do anything to help her."
    n "リリーは華子の幸せを心から気にかけているけど、実際俺に華子の手助けができるわけじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2688
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_cc918a55:

    # n "As far as I can tell, her scars don't hold her back physically, and everyone I've met seems to have overcome their disabilities to some extent."
    n "俺が見る限りでは、華子の傷跡は彼女の身体に不具合をもたらすものではないし、今までに出会ったどの人も、それぞれある程度は自分の障害を克服している。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2690
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_16bc7f3a:

    # n "I don't have any ulterior motives to hang out with Hanako, we just share similar interests."
    n "俺は何か魂胆があって華子と一緒にいるわけじゃない。ただ単に趣味が近いってだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2692
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_384a99ca:

    # n "{vspace=30}Isn't that enough?"
    n "\nそれで十分じゃないのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2695
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_76b2fe88_3:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2701
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_481c50c2:

    # li "So, Hisao, are you enjoying yourself?"
    li "久夫さん、楽しんでいますか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2703
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_74a703c9:

    # "Lilly's words break me out of my reverie, and I take a second to reconsider where I am."
    "リリーの言葉で、俺は物思いから現実に引き戻される。自分がどこにいるのかを認識するのに数秒かかる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2705
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_ae16d3cd:

    # "I'm in a room with two girls in their bedclothes. This is something to be enjoyed."
    "寝間着を着た二人の女の子と一緒に部屋の中にいるんだ。楽しまなくてどうする。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2707
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_2a2dc2c5:

    # hi "Yeah, it's relaxing. Almost like I'm not in the school any more. Do you do this often?"
    hi "ああ、リラックスしてるよ。もう学校の中じゃないみたいだよ。こういうのはちょくちょくやってるのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2712
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_5e493ced:

    # li "Quite often, but not as often as we take tea in the school building."
    li "ええ、頻繁に。さすがに学校でお茶を飲む頻度には劣りますが"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2714
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_37a9ee7a:

    # "Considering they do that nearly every day, that's not a big surprise."
    "ほぼ毎日学校でお茶会を開いている二人を見れば、驚くことじゃない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2716
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_fd62a08a:

    # "As I move to take another sip from my teacup, I find it sadly empty."
    "俺はもう一口飲もうとカップを覗き込むけど、残念なことに、空になってしまっていた。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2718
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_65e60fd2:

    # hi "That was delicious. Thank you Hanako, Lilly."
    hi "おいしかったよ。ありがとう、華子、リリー"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2723
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_eb14f811:

    # ha "You're welcome."
    ha "どういたしまして"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2728
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_8c7bed9e:

    # li "Yes, you're most welcome Hisao. It's nice to have a third person here."
    li "はい、どういたしまして、久夫さん。三人目のメンバーが増えて嬉しいです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2730
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_3edce04d:

    # hi "Well, any time you need someone to fill that position, I'm always available. Always."
    hi "えーと、その席を埋める人が必要になったら、いつでも呼んでくれよ。いつでもだ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2732
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_1aad795e:

    # "One must be sure to get one's point across in these circumstances."
    "こういう状況だ、大事なことはちゃんと念押ししておかないとな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2738
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_01a88cb9:

    # "Lilly lets loose a yawn, which she unsuccessfully hides with her hand."
    "リリーがあくびを漏らす。手で口を覆うけど隠し切れていない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2743
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_df62ad4d:

    # li "Pardon me, I think I'm a little tired."
    li "ごめんなさい、少し疲れているみたいです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2748
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_656ff99b:

    # ha "I think we're all a little tired…"
    ha "みんなそうだと思う……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2753
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_3de06da5:

    # li "My my, how astute we are tonight, Hanako."
    li "あらあら、今夜は良く気がつくのね、華ちゃん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2758
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_18bf72c9:

    # li "We really should head to bed; we all have class tomorrow."
    li "本当に寝たほうがいいですね、明日も授業がありますし"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2760
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_874537c4:

    # hi "Yeah… I should go."
    hi "うん……そうする"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2765
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_5622699f:

    # li "Thank you for your presence, Hisao."
    li "いらしてくれてありがとうございました、久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2770
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_b90df44e:

    # ha "Th… thanks. You'll come again?"
    ha "あ……ありがと。また来てくれる？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2772
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_927ea77b:

    # hi "Not even a whole army could stop me."
    hi "万難を排して参上するよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2777
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_df338e79:

    # li "I'm impressed by your determination, Hisao."
    li "その決意に感動しました。久夫さん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2779
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_2af7bba8:

    # hi "Either way, you're right. We'd best get going."
    hi "どっちにしろ、リリーの言うとおりだ。もう帰ったほうがいいな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2781
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_c4789be2:

    # "I stand up, and make for the door."
    "俺は立ち上がると、ドアのほうへ向かう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2786
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_5e7d84cf:

    # "Hanako gingerly stands up behind me."
    "華子が俺の後ろで慎重に立ち上がる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2788
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_5f031343:

    # "I stop and face her."
    "俺は立ち止まり、華子に顔を向ける。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2790
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_f3b42fd8:

    # hi "Are you coming with me?"
    hi "一緒に来るのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2797
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_8085a3c1:

    # "Hanako instantly blossoms into full blush."
    "華子が途端に真っ赤になる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2802
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_e45f7741:

    # ha "No… I… not… this room… isn't…"
    ha "ちが……私……違う……この部屋……じゃなくて……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2804
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_48ff747d:

    # hi "It's okay, I was only joking."
    hi "わかってるよ、ただの冗談だ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2809
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_5ad8a756:

    # ha "Oh… okay… good night…"
    ha "あぅ……うん……おやすみ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2814
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_7e7c816d:

    # li "Good night, Hanako. Good night, Hisao."
    li "おやすみなさい、華ちゃん。久夫さんも"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2816
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_67158daf:

    # hi "Night all."
    hi "おやすみ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2818
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_6de05866:

    # "And with that, our tea party finishes."
    "そうして、お茶会はお開きとなった。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2823
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_7891cde9:

    # "I'm still not sure what it is that Lilly wants me to do for Hanako, but I don't want to let her down."
    "俺はまだ、リリーが俺に華子のために何をしてほしいのかがわからないでいる。でもリリーを失望させたくはない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2825
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_a5404c5c:

    # "I wait until the door has closed behind us before turning to Hanako."
    "ドアが後ろで閉まるのを待ってから、俺は華子へと向き直る。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2830
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_c6b2c385:

    # hi "Hey, Hanako, you know, you don't have to be nervous around me or anything."
    hi "なあ華子、前に言ったろ？　俺と一緒にいるときには気を張る必要なんかないって"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2832
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_432fb44c:

    # hi "I mean, we're friends, right?"
    hi "つまりだな、俺たちは友達じゃないか。な？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2837
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_dc9ff3a5:

    # ha "R-right. We're… friends."
    ha "う、うん。友達……だね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2839
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_9e235b22:

    # hi "If you ever want to hang out or anything, just let me know. We still need to have that chess rematch, remember?"
    hi "もし遊んだりしたくなったら、俺に言ってくれよ。チェスの再戦だってしなきゃいけないだろ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2844
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_74d620de:

    # ha "S-sure…"
    ha "う、うん……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2849
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_a86606d5:

    # ha "B-but I don't think you'll win…"
    ha "で、でも、久夫くん……勝てないと思うけど……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2851
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_eed198ca:

    # hi "It wouldn't be any fun if it was easy."
    hi "簡単に勝てちゃったらつまらないだろ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2856
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_81831ea4:

    # "Hanako seems to give a muted laugh, but she could have just as easily been exhaling."
    "華子は抑えた声で笑ったように見えたけど、単に息を吐いただけかもしれない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2858
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_9ddb4683:

    # ha "G-good night Hisao…"
    ha "お、おやすみ、久夫くん……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2869
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_094aae14:

    # "With that, Hanako quickly retreats into her room, located next to Lilly's."
    "そういうと華子は急いでリリーの部屋の隣にある自分の部屋に戻る。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2871
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_446a4a22:

    # "I start to walk back to my dorm, but the simple act of walking seems to drain me of my energy."
    "俺も自分の寮へと歩き始めるけど、歩くという単純な行為さえ俺の体力を奪っていくように感じる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2876
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_9f4b3a07:

    # "I barely make it to my room before I am hit by a wave of exhaustion."
    "かろうじて自分の部屋にたどり着くと、疲労感の波が押し寄せてくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2883
translate jp a2_hanako_mad_hatter_6b5aa2ed:

    # "I kick off my shoes, fall into bed and fall asleep by the time my head hits the pillow."
    "靴を脱ぎ、ベッドに倒れこむ。枕に頭が触れる頃には、もう夢の世界へと旅立っていた。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2897
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_414460c8:

    # "I pull my door closed, ready for another day of classes."
    "自室を出てドアを閉める。今日の授業の準備は万端だ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2907
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_4ba5b253:

    # ke "Sleep well?"
    ke "よく寝てるか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2911
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_00e9df53:

    # "Kenji's sudden arrival makes me jump, and I narrowly avoid butting heads with him."
    "健二がいきなり現れたので俺は飛び上がってしまう。かろうじて健二と頭同士をぶつけそうになるのを回避する。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2913
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_67f74c55:

    # "I know he has poor eyesight, but he knows who I am now. Does he still have to stand this close?"
    "健二の視力はとても悪い。でももう俺のことはわかっている。だったらこんな近くに立っている必要はあるのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2918
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_20f63de6:

    # hi "Oh. Yeah. Like a baby."
    hi "ああ、うん。赤ちゃんみたいにな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2923
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_7ef7182e:

    # ke "Damn, why do people say that? Have you ever heard a baby sleep?"
    ke "ふん、なんでみんなそう言うんだ？　寝ている赤ん坊を知らないのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2925
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_0fd006f7:

    # ke "They scream. All night. Every night. Babies don't sleep well, ever."
    ke "奴らは泣き叫ぶんだ。一晩中。毎晩だぞ。赤ん坊がよく眠ることなんてないんだよ、決してな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2927
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_c2bbf865:

    # "Well, there goes my restful state. I have to remember to never use figures of speech with Kenji."
    "あーあ、俺の安息はどこかに行っちまった。二度と健二に比喩表現を使わないようにしないとな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2929
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_8bd4126a:

    # hi "All right, I get your point. It was a figure of speech."
    hi "あーわかった、わかったから。もののたとえだよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2934
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_18739701:

    # ke "Yeah, sure, whatever. Where were you last night? I had a favor to ask but you weren't around."
    ke "ああ、まあ、なんでもいいや。昨日の夜はどこに行ってたんだ？　頼みごとがあったのに、どこにもいなかったじゃねえか"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2936
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_c7b163d4:

    # "For a split second I consider telling Kenji the truth; that I was spending time with Hanako and Lilly."
    "一瞬、華子とリリーと一緒にいたという真実を言おうかと考える。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2938
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_165818f1:

    # "Thankfully, that split second passes as soon as it came."
    "ありがたいことに、その一瞬はその名の通り瞬く間に過ぎ行く。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2940
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_fbaeb729:

    # hi "I was just out. Checking out the local area and stuff. You know, recon."
    hi "出かけてただけだよ。このあたりを散策してたんだ。ほら、『偵察』だ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2945
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_1055dda8:

    # ke "Good man, good. I knew you were the type to plan ahead…"
    ke "上出来だ、よくやったぞ。やっぱりお前は計画性のある奴だったな……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2947
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_b30f047b:

    # hi "Anyway, what was this favor you wanted?"
    hi "ところで、頼みごとってなんだったんだ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2952
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_3c9a2998:

    # ke "I was going to get some take-out, but I needed change."
    ke "食い物をテイクアウトしようと思ってな、金が必要だったんだ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2954
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_1e70c0bb:

    # hi "Wait, what? I gave you money last week and you still haven't paid me back!"
    hi "待て、なんだって？　お前、先週貸した金もまだ返してないじゃないか！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2959
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_2d15fe9e:

    # ke "Tch, and I was starting to think you were cool."
    ke "チッ、お前はいいやつだと思い始めていたのに"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2961
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_051e9fee:

    # "Kenji fishes around in his pocket and produces his wallet."
    "健二はポケットをまさぐり、財布を取り出す。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2963
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_f8765421:

    # "As he counts out the 400 yen he owes me, I can clearly see at least two 10,000 yen notes."
    "健二が俺に借金している４００円を数えて出す時に、財布の中に少なくとも１万円札が２枚あるのが見える。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2965
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_33b2e1d9:

    # hi "Hey, what the hell? Why are you borrowing money off me when you've got that much cash?"
    hi "おい、どういうことだ？　なんでそんなに金があるのに返さないんだよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2967
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_d12370b9:

    # "Kenji hisses a little, realizing that he's been had."
    "金を持っていることを見とがめられて、健二は不満そうに小さく『シッ』と舌を鳴らす。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2969
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_810df696:

    # ke "Get off my case, man. It's bad luck to break a big note for anything less than half its value. It's the tycoon's rule."
    ke "お前には関係ねえだろ。額面の半分以下の買い物をするのにデカい札を崩すのは縁起が悪いんだ。それが資本家のルールだ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2971
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_f6977ad0:

    # ke "Last night's dinner is going to cost me seven years of bad luck. Seven years!"
    ke "昨日の夕飯のおかげで俺は７年不運になるんだ。７年だぞ！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2976
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_b324007c:

    # ke "Don't you think that's enough cause to help someone out? I'd get a shorter sentence if I just stole the stuff."
    ke "誰かを助ける理由には十分だと思わないのか？　そのブツをただ盗んだとしても、そっちの刑のほうがまだ短いんだぞ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2978
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_9cade674:

    # "My common sense screams at me to say something to him, but thankfully I restrain myself."
    "俺の中の常識が健二に何か言い返せと叫ぶけれど、ありがたいことに俺はそれを抑え込む。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2980
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_133c5cd9:

    # "Arguing a point like this with Kenji will just lead to further and more complicated discussions."
    "この類のことを健二と議論しても、余計に会話がこんがらがるだけだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2982
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_983456a8:

    # hi "Yeah, I guess you're right. Maybe you should plan these things a little better?"
    hi "ああ、まあそうかもな。金については、もう少しよく計画を立てたほうがいいんじゃないか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2987
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_a2e7404e:

    # ke "Yeah man, I know. But I've just got so much stuff to do, it's hard. And you're never around any more so I'm on my own."
    ke "ああ、わかってる。でもやることがあまりに多くてな、大変なんだ。それに最近お前が全然いないから、俺一人でやるしかないんだよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2989
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_05c4b193:

    # ke "We're supposed to be brothers in brotherhood, remember?"
    ke "俺たちは同志の中の同志だろ？　覚えてるか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2991
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_fbd10166:

    # hi "Yeah yeah, I get you. Global conspiracy and such. I'll keep my ear to the ground."
    hi "ああ、うん、わかってるよ。世界的陰謀とかなんとか。噂には敏感であろうと思ってるよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:2996
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_e506da83:

    # "Kenji draws close enough for me to get a clear whiff of his garlic-tainted breath."
    "健二はニンニクが腐ったような息の臭いがはっきり感じられるほど近くに近づいてくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3001
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_7b669498:

    # ke "You'd better, man. You're already spending less time here. That's the first thing they do."
    ke "まったくだぞ、お前。最近留守にしてばっかりじゃねえか。これは奴らが最初にやる手口だぞ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3003
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_170906f1:

    # ke "They'll try to split us up. Divide and conquer. Sun Tzu said that."
    ke "奴らは俺たちを分裂させようとするだろう。分裂させて征服せよ。孫子の言葉だ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3005
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_142214b4:

    # hi "Roger that. Now, I've got to be going. I've got classes. You coming?"
    hi "オーケー、よくわかった。さて、もう行かないと。授業があるからな。お前は行くのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3010
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_23061b4f:

    # ke "Nah, I'm tired. I stayed up all night just to make sure nothing was going to happen after splitting that note."
    ke "いや、疲れたし。あの札を崩しても何も起こらないことを確かめるのに徹夜してたからな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3012
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_df06d837:

    # hi "As rational as ever, I see."
    hi "了解。相変わらず合理的なことで"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3017
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_bf3b976c:

    # ke "Whatever. Night."
    ke "まあな。おやすみ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3028
translate jp a2_hanako_small_change_5e8bf7f4:

    # "Kenji scurries back into his room, and I hear him throwing his locks as I walk down the hallway."
    "健二は急ぎ足で自室に戻る。俺が廊下を下っていると、奴が鍵をかける音が聞こえてきた。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3042
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_a5ef963c:

    # mu "…that is why some people can't roll their tongue, or why their second toe is longer than their big toe."
    mu "……そのようなことから巻き舌ができない人がいたり、その人たちの足の人差し指が親指より長かったりするわけだ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3044
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_2d0d59fd:

    # "Mutou beams a half-moon smile at us, obviously proud of his explanation of recessive genes."
    "武藤先生が自信たっぷりに劣性遺伝子の説明をしながら微笑みを向けてくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3046
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_86a5f305:

    # "However, no matter how impressed he is at the science that defines who we are, the classroom seems to be reduced to a stupor."
    "でも先生が俺たちを定義する科学にいくら感動したところで、教室内は昏睡状態のようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3048
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_70e4914a:

    # "Why is it that a bad explanation can make even the most interesting thing seem worthless?"
    "世界で一番面白いことであっても、説明が下手くそだと何の価値もないように見えてしまうのはどうしてだろう？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3053
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_b9f79c47:

    # "I can see Mutou deflate as he realizes that nothing he's said in the past half hour has sunk in."
    "先生がここ３０分で自分が話したことが全く伝わっていないことに気がついて肩を落とすのが見える。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3058
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_92d824a6:

    # "Whispered conversations start to break the silence, and like an avalanche, the noise level in the class starts to rise."
    "コソコソ話が始まり静寂を破ると、雪崩のようにその音量が大きくなっていく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3063
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_ff265982:

    # "Defeated, Mutou identifies some questions from the text book and sets to clearing off the blackboard."
    "心が折られた先生は教科書から問題をいくつか指定すると黒板を消し始める。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3068
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_88d11e22:

    # "Almost as if expected, Hanako packs up her things and leaves as soon as people start talking and laughing among themselves."
    "皆が談笑を始めるころには、ほとんど予定していたかのように華子は荷物をまとめて教室を出て行く。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3070
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_c6e110d8:

    # "The initial shock of seeing someone play so blatantly truant has started to fade, but it doesn't stop me from wondering."
    "初めてこんな露骨に授業をサボるのを見たときの衝撃は薄れてしまったけど、今でも驚きがないわけではない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3072
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_f039a358:

    # "Is she leaving because she doesn't want people to speak to her? Or is it just the thought of people around her shattering her peace?"
    "華子は話しかけられたくないから教室を出て行くのか？　それとも単に周りの人間の考え方が彼女の平穏を壊すのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3077
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_4637668b:

    # "Before I can think about the topic any further, the lunch bells ring. I wonder if she was simply taking the opportunity to leave early."
    "それ以上考える前に、昼休みの鐘が鳴る。華子は単にこの機会を利用して早退しただけなのだろうか。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3079
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_67505965:

    # "The usual clamor of students exchanging books for lunch reverberates around the room, and while Misha is distracted, I grab my lunch and head out the door."
    "生徒たちが教科書と昼飯を入れ替えるいつもの喧騒が教室内に反響し、ミーシャの気がそれている間に、俺は昼飯を手にしてドアの外へ向かう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3089
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_13e977ed:

    # "Lilly already sits in the tea room, setting out her lunch alone."
    "既にリリーがいつもの紅茶の部屋で一人で昼飯を広げて席についている。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3091
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_f27359ae:

    # hi "So, Hanako's not here then?"
    hi "あれ、華子はいないのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3096
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_c18236b6:

    # li "Oh, Hisao, how are you? I haven't met Hanako since this morning, I'm afraid."
    li "あら久夫さん、こんにちは。あいにく、華ちゃんとは今朝以来会っていないんですよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3098
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_ac291dd0:

    # "That's right, Hanako and Lilly live next to each other."
    "そうだ、華子とリリーは部屋が隣同士だった。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3100
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_a7fdd4ca:

    # "Somehow I think their morning conversations are slightly more grounded than Kenji's ramblings."
    "同じ『朝の会話』なのに、リリーたちのそれは健二の散漫な演説に比べてもう少し落ち着いたものだと感じるのはなんでだろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3102
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_4a4a0911:

    # hi "That's strange. She left class early, so I figured that she'd come here."
    hi "おかしいな。先に授業を抜けていったから、ここに来てるものだと思っていたんだけどな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3107
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_b6cb230a:

    # li "So she's still leaving class early…"
    li "やっぱりまだ早抜けしているんですか……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3109
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_febb31e4:

    # hi "Huh? Yeah, I've seen her do it a few times."
    hi "へ？　ああ。今までに何回か見たな"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3116
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_72d51a90:

    # "Lilly drops her head a little, and her tone of voice is notably depressed. It's very reminiscent of someone who is used to hearing bad news."
    "リリーが少し頭を垂れる。その声のトーンは明らかに下がっている。その様子は『またですか』と言わんばかりだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3118
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_2d4a5daa:

    # li "I was so sure that she'd stop doing that once you two became friends."
    li "久夫さんと友達になってしまえば華ちゃんは早抜けをやめるだろうと私は確信していたんです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3123
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_9ebd35ba:

    # li "Everyone has their own pace, I suppose."
    li "まあ、人には皆、自分のペースがありますよね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3125
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_eb348c7b:

    # hi "Well, I was wondering about just that today. Why exactly does she leave?"
    hi "ああ、俺も今日、ちょうどそのことが気になってたんだ。華子が早抜けする具体的な理由はなんなんだ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3130
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_8d8c209e:

    # li "I'm not entirely sure myself. I personally think it's because she doesn't want to be put in a situation where she has to answer someone."
    li "確信があるわけではないんですが、華ちゃんは誰かの質問に答えなくてはならない状況に居たくないのでは、と個人的には思いますね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3132
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_18509307:

    # "I have a flashback of my first meeting with her, when I thought she looked like a cornered animal. Maybe I wasn't far from the truth."
    "初めて華子と出会った時のことがフラッシュバックする。あのとき俺は華子が追いつめられた動物のように見えていた。その考えは完全に間違いってわけじゃなかったのかもしれないな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3134
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_376a7ec2:

    # hi "But she seems fine with talking to you, and with me… a bit…"
    hi "でもリリーと話しているときは大丈夫そうじゃないか。俺とのときも……ほんの少しだけは……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3139
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_027f0015:

    # li "It's a little more complex than that. I imagine that the first thing most people ask her about is her scars, and what happened."
    li "それほど単純ではないんです。たいていの人は、華ちゃんにまず傷跡のこと、そして何があったのかを尋ねるだろうと思います"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3141
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_2e968ca2:

    # li "She rarely talks about it with me, but I can tell that she doesn't like to remember whatever happened back then."
    li "華ちゃんは私に傷跡の話をほとんどしませんが、そのとき起こったことを思い出したくないのだということはわかります"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3146
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_feee00ed:

    # li "Leaving class and running away from discussions is her preemptive strike, if you will."
    li "授業の早抜けや話し合いから逃げ出すのは言うなれば、先手を打っているようなものなんです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3148
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_cb207f84:

    # hi "Huh… so then how does that explain her talking to me?"
    hi "うーん……じゃあ俺と話してることはどう説明すればいいんだ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3153
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_8a0498bf:

    # li "You said it yourself yesterday at breakfast; you tried to ignore her scars. Once she saw that you weren't going to ask her about that, she opened herself up to you."
    li "久夫さん自身が昨日の朝食の時に言っていたじゃないですか。華ちゃんの傷跡に気づかないようにした、と。華ちゃんは久夫さんが傷跡のことを何も聞こうとしなかったのを見て、心を開いたんです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3155
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_653ef7f0:

    # hi "Hrm, I guess you're right. Maybe. I dunno. You know her better than I, so I'll take your word for it."
    hi "ふむ、リリーの言う通りかもね。たぶん。わからないや。リリーのほうが華子のことをよく知ってるし、リリーの言うことを信じるよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3162
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_e0b5d357:

    # li "I wouldn't worry about that. I'm sure you'll come to know her as well as I do soon enough."
    li "それについては心配していませんよ。きっとじきに私と同じくらい華ちゃんのことがわかるようになりますから"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3167
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_80d87810:

    # li "I welcome the prospect of her having a new friend, and the two of you have such similar interests…"
    li "華ちゃんが新しい友達を持つことは大歓迎です。二人ともとてもよく似た趣味を持ってますし……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3169
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_c800c091:

    # hi "Well, I hardly count reading as a team sport. It is good to have company, though."
    hi "まあ、読書はチームでやるもののうちには入らないと思うよ。ただ仲間がいるっていうのはいいもんだね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3174
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_f8905f40:

    # li "That's my point. Hanako is still an average person at heart. She also wants company at times like that."
    li "それです。華ちゃんは実際にはまだ普通の子なんです。時にはそういう仲間が欲しいはずです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3176
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_c9c67089:

    # hi "Huh, I see. I think. To be honest, both of you still confuse me a little."
    hi "うーん、わかった。そうだな。正直言って二人には今でもちょっと戸惑うことがあるよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3181
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_37c38658:

    # li "That's only natural, Hisao. We've only known each other for a little while; it's unreasonable to expect you to understand us, just as we can't understand you."
    li "当たり前ですよ、久夫さん。私たちは知り合ってまだほんのわずかですから。私たちが久夫さんのことを理解できないのと同じで、久夫さんが私たちのことを理解してくれると期待するのには無理があります"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3186
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_2fcfb65b:

    # li "But that is half the fun of becoming friends, right?"
    li "だけど、それも友達になることの楽しみのうちですよね？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3188
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_00cdd77f:

    # hi "Yes, yes it is."
    hi "ああ、そうだね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3193
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_666b085a:

    # li "Although… I suppose there is the matter of us being opposite genders. Men and women do seem to confuse each other quite often."
    li "とはいえ……私たちが異性であることの問題もあると思います。本当に、男性と女性はいつも互いを惑わせるみたいです"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3195
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_b6ee6083:

    # "She says this with a light giggle, finding amusement at the odd little details of life."
    "ちょっとした人生のおかしさに慰みを見いだしたのか、リリーは軽く笑いながら言う。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3200
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_6d0a7ee4:

    # li "I hope you don't mind, but I'm going to start eating."
    li "もし差し支えなければ、私はお昼を食べますけど"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3202
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_b30cddcd:

    # hi "No, go ahead, I think I'll eat something too. I've got some books I want to drop back at the library before classes start, so I'd better get a move on."
    hi "ああ、どうぞどうぞ。俺も食べるとするかな。午後の授業が始まる前に図書室に返したい本があるから、急がないと"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3207
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_8788f0b1:

    # li "You'll probably find Hanako there as well. If you do see her, can you tell her to stop by my room later tonight? I'd like to talk to her."
    li "たぶん華ちゃんもそこで見つかると思います。もし見かけたら、今夜私の部屋に来るように言っておいていただけないでしょうか？　華ちゃんとお話がしたいので"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3209
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_db0c25a0:

    # hi "You're not coming?"
    hi "リリーは図書室に来ないのか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3214
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_c3ad30ae:

    # li "Unfortunately I have a class representatives' meeting later, so I'll be gone as soon as I've finished my lunch."
    li "残念ですがこのあと学級委員の会議があるんですよ。なので、食べ終わったらすぐにそちらに行かなくてはなりません"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3216
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_94008d93:

    # hi "Okay then, if I don't see her in the library then I'll tell her in class. I'm sure she'll be back after lunch."
    hi "了解。じゃあもし図書室で華子を見なかったら教室で言っておくよ。華子も昼休みが終わったら教室に戻ってると思うし"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3218
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_0ee52a58:

    # "We fall silent as we start to eat, and I take a second to reflect on our conversation."
    "俺たちは食事を再開し、部屋の中には沈黙が落ちる。俺は今の会話について少しのあいだ思いをめぐらす。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3220
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_6740b049:

    # "I've always thought that Hanako's shyness was simply due to her being self-conscious of her scars."
    "俺はいつも、華子の内気な性格は彼女がその傷跡を気にし過ぎているせいでそうなっているのだと思ってきた。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3222
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_d2fe5666:

    # "But that is a pretty superficial way of looking at her."
    "だけど、それは華子に対する極めて表面的な見方だ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3224
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_ca1b8f85:

    # "Just when I thought I was able to see through the fog of Lilly and Hanako, I realize that I'm more lost than when I started."
    "リリーと華子の心の霧の向こう側を見ることができたと思ったまさにそのとき、俺は最初よりもさらにわからなくなっていることに気がつく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3226
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_f2ef4006:

    # "Lilly quickly finishes her lunch, acutely aware of her meeting. I don't blame her."
    "リリーは会議を強く意識して手早く昼食を食べ終え、俺もそれを咎めない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3228
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_dfa74fe6:

    # "Shizune is most likely going to be there, and I doubt she wants to give her the satisfaction of another argument."
    "間違いなく静音も会議に出ているだろう。リリーがまた静音に議論を仕掛けられることを望んでいるとは思えない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3233
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_cffbe383:

    # li "I must be off. Same time tomorrow?"
    li "もう行かないといけません。明日もこの時間に？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3235
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_55189750:

    # hi "Same time, same channel. I'd better head off too; I don't want to risk being late."
    hi "同じ時間に、チャンネルもそのままさ。俺もそろそろ行ったほうがいいな、遅刻するのは避けたいし"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3245
translate jp a2_hanako_absenteeism_9e97d45e:

    # "Lilly smiles gently, picks up her cane and walks out into the hall."
    "リリーは優しく微笑むと、杖を手に取り廊下へと出て行く。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3254
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_5c2dc0ea:

    # "I turn my back on Lilly as we head in opposite directions. For some reason I find myself hoping she doesn't get into another fight with Shizune."
    "俺はリリーに背を向け互いに反対方向へと向かう。どういうわけか、リリーがまた静音とけんかをしなければいいけどと願っている自分に気づく。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3256
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_8df37b47:

    # "As much as I like Lilly, Shizune and Misha have been pretty instrumental in helping me adjust, even if half of our conversations are thinly-veiled recruitment attempts."
    "リリーは大切な友人だと思っているけど、静音とミーシャも俺が山久に慣れるのを大いに手助けしてくれている。たとえ会話の半分が見え透いた生徒会への勧誘だったとしてもだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3258
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_d2d4462e:

    # "Then again, I barely know either of them. Maybe they were previously leaders of some kind of secret society, but their love for each other drove them apart…"
    "でも、俺はリリーのことも静音のこともほとんど知らない。もしかしたら二人は以前なにかの秘密結社の指導者で、でもお互いへの愛が二人を引き裂いてしまって……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3260
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_da6bfc95:

    # "Man, I need to stop reading cheap fiction. It's rotting my brain. Either that or I've got to move away from Kenji and his bad influence."
    "まったく、安っぽいフィクションを読むのはやめなきゃだめだな。脳が腐る。そうでなければ、健二とあいつが及ぼす悪影響から距離を置かないと。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3262
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_11a6205a:

    # "It's sad that I can't tell the two apart any more."
    "もはやこの２つを区別できないのが悲しい。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3269
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_cc6423aa:

    # "I slide my books down the return chute and they crash into the cart with a pleasant thud."
    "借りた本を返却ポストへ入れると、中のカートにぶつかって小気味いい音を立てる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3276
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_ba97ce0e:

    # "Yuuko, however, doesn't seem as impressed as I."
    "しかし優子さんは俺と同じようには感じなかったみたいだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3278
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_2692f86d:

    # yu "H-Hisao! You scared me!"
    yu "な、中井くん！　脅かさないで！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3280
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_bcb4e532:

    # hi "Sorry, I thought you would be used to that by now. Or is the literacy level here so low that nobody borrows any books?"
    hi "すいません、慣れてるものだと思って。それとも山久の生徒の読解力が低すぎるせいで誰も本を借りないとか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3285
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_a83143dc:

    # yu "Huh? No I think everyone here can read fine…"
    yu "へ？　ここの生徒はみんな字は読めると思うけど……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3287
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_e99e2a3c:

    # hi "Yeah… never mind."
    hi "ああ……忘れてください"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3289
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_6c4c9be3:

    # "There are some battles that you can never win. Trying to explain jokes is one of them. My Dad taught me that the hard way."
    "勝ち目がない戦いというものがある。冗談を説明するのはそのひとつだ。そのことは自分の父親に思い知らされた。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3291
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_674d9c65:

    # hi "Say, Yuuko, have you seen Hanako about? She left class early but she wasn't in her usual hiding place."
    hi "ところで、優子さん。華子を見ませんでしたか？　授業を早抜けしてたんですけど、いつもの隠れ家に居なかったから"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3296
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_9a1b83cd:

    # yu "I think I saw her sneak in before lunch…"
    yu "昼休み前にこっそり入ってくるのを見たと思うんだけど……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3301
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_5e531f24:

    # yu "Oh! But I'm not supposed to tell anyone that!"
    yu "あっ！　でもそんなこと人に言っちゃいけないんだった！"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3303
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_6cac9a59:

    # hi "I just told you that I saw her leave, no need to stress out…"
    hi "俺はただ『華子が出て行くのを見た』って言っただけです。そんなに慌てなくても大丈夫ですよ……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3308
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_0bc10676:

    # yu "Oh… of course. She's probably in the back."
    yu "あ……そうだね。華子ちゃんならたぶん奥の方にいると思うわ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3310
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_23326cfe:

    # hi "Thanks. Get any new books in recently?"
    hi "ありがとうございます。最近新しい本は入りましたか？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3315
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_575cb9c9:

    # yu "No, sorry. I'll let you know when we do, though."
    yu "ううん、ごめんね。でも、もし新しいものが入ったら教えるから"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3317
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_16a7dec2:

    # hi "Okay."
    hi "そっか"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3319
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_2d2554e6:

    # "If there's one thing I know about librarians, part-time or otherwise, it's that they appreciate people who take a genuine interest in their work."
    "俺が司書について知っていることが１つあるとすれば、その人がバイトであれ何であれ、自分たちの仕事に心から興味を持っている人間を理解してくれるということだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3327
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_841b50b9:

    # "I walk the now-familiar path to Hanako's reading nook, picking out a few titles along the way."
    "華子が読書をしている部屋の隅へと続く、今では見慣れた道のりを進む。途中で本を何冊か選び出す。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3329
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_48dbde7d:

    # "Sometimes I find it hard to discover a book that will interest me among the shelves. An author's name and a two-word title don't mean much in a sea of similar words."
    "本棚から面白そうな本を見つけるのが大変だと感じることがある。著者名と２語くらいの題名じゃ、似たような単語ばかり並んでいる中ではあまり意味がない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3331
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_0e555f9a:

    # "For that reason, I sometimes re-read books that I read in the past. Better to bet on the favorite than a new runner."
    "だから俺は時々過去に読んだことのある本を読み直す。初顔よりもお気に入りの馬に賭けたほうがいいってことだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3333
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_40cdad86:

    # "An unfamiliar title from a familiar author peeks out among the spines of its neighbors, so I remove it from the shelf."
    "よく知っている著者だけど、まだ読んだことのないタイトルの本の背表紙が目にとまり、俺はそれを本棚から引き出す。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3335
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_323ebc25:

    # "At least I'm not going over old material."
    "まあ、古い本を読み直すわけじゃないしな。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3340
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_3a836703:

    # "As expected, Hanako sits on her beanbag, buried deep in a copy of 'Dance Dance Dance.'"
    "予想通り、華子はいつものクッションに座り、『ダンス・ダンス・ダンス』という本に頭をつっこむようにして読書にのめりこんでいる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3342
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_d5ff4c39:

    # hi "Hi Hanako. How's it going?"
    hi "よう華子。調子はどうだ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3344
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_0e7a2da3:

    # "I fight back the urge to ask why she left class early. If Lilly's suspicions were right, then asking her about that could have the opposite effect."
    "俺はなんで授業を早抜けしたのかを聞きたくなる衝動を抑える。もしリリーの予想が正しければ、逆効果になる可能性がある。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3346
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_3d528b66:

    # "Best to leave it for the time being. Sometimes the best way to get an answer from someone is to never ask the question."
    "さしあたりこのことには触れないでおくのがベストだ。『何も聞かない』というのが、ときには誰かから答えを聞き出すための最善の方法になることもある。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3351
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_fbc1a5ee:

    # ha "Hello, H-Hisao. I'm fine."
    ha "こんにちは、ひ、久夫くん。元気だよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3353
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_1442a777:

    # "Something seems off, and after a couple of seconds, I realize what it is. Hanako's smiling."
    "なんだか違和感を感じて、数秒後にその正体に気づく。華子が微笑んでいる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3355
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_ee8d27a8:

    # "She looks as if she's pleased to see me. It's a nice change from the usual, instinctively frightened reaction, and something I hope I can see more of as we get to know each other better."
    "華子は俺に会えたことに喜んでいるように見える。いつもの本能で怯えているような反応から考えると良い変化だし、俺もお互いをもっと知るためにこれからもその笑顔が見れればいいなと思う。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3357
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_3ebf617c:

    # hi "Good to hear. How's that book? I've heard it's a trip."
    hi "そりゃよかった。その本はどんな感じだ？　旅をする物語だってのは聞いたことがあるけど"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3359
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_7ce63cc2:

    # ha "I-it's good… I think."
    ha "お、おもしろいと……思うよ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3361
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_879bd045:

    # ha "I've only j-just started it, so I d-don't really know."
    ha "よ、読み始めたばかりだから、全部は、わ、わからないけど"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3363
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_2aefd36e:

    # hi "Fair enough. Let me know how it goes; I may borrow it once you're done."
    hi "いいよいいよ。読み終わったらどうだったか教えてくれよ。後で俺も借りるかもしれないからさ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3365
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_ff70d1cd:

    # ha "S-sure."
    ha "う、うん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3367
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_6e5ab4a7:

    # "There's a good fifteen minutes left in lunch. Not enough to really get into a book, but too much to stand around doing nothing."
    "昼休みは１５分残っている。本当に本にのめりこむには少々短いけど、何もしないでいるのは手持ち無沙汰だ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3372
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_099755f6:

    # "And Hanako's already returned to her reading, so I doubt I'll get much conversation from her."
    "華子は既に読書を再開していて、あまり会話をすることは期待できそうにない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3374
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_74bf9165:

    # "Oh well, I'd better make myself comfortable."
    "まあいいか、俺は俺でくつろぐとしよう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3378
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_26e24156:

    # "I slouch into a beanbag and crack open my book."
    "俺はソファに座って前かがみになり、自分の持ってきた本を開く。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3380
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_7677bb0b:

    # "The familiar style of the author leaps out at me from the very first line. As the sentences turn into paragraphs, I start to relax a little."
    "作者のいつも通りの執筆スタイルが１行目から目に飛び込んで来る。文、段落と読み進めるうちに俺は徐々にリラックスしてくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3384
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_22e4f130:

    # "But no matter how I try, I can't seem to get myself into the atmosphere of the book."
    "だけどどう頑張っても、本の雰囲気に浸ることはできそうにない。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3386
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_255a61dd:

    # "This is partly due to the lack of time, but the more distracting factor is Hanako."
    "時間が無いせいでもあるけど、俺の気を散らすより大きな原因は華子だ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3394
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_640b70b1:

    # "Every ten or so seconds she peers over the top of her book, but when our eyes meet she quickly ducks behind the covers."
    "１０秒かそこらおきに華子が本の上越しにこちらを見てくるのだけど、俺と目が合うと瞬時にカバーの後ろに隠れてしまう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3396
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_999fbeb1:

    # "I guess she did want to talk about something after all."
    "やっぱり華子は俺と何か話したいんじゃないのか。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3401
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_f8f384f1:

    # hi "What's up? You look like a prairie dog on lookout."
    hi "どうした？　見張り中のプレーリードッグみたいだぞ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3408
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_f630accd:

    # ha "N-… it's nothing."
    ha "な……なんでもない"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3410
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_608f5117:

    # hi "I've told you before, 'nothing' means 'something' when you say it like that."
    hi "前に言ったよな？　そうやって華子が『なんでもない』って言うときは『なにかある』って"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3415
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_aec32af1:

    # "Hanako squirms a little in her beanbag, hoping that by changing her position she'll find the words she's looking for."
    "体勢を変えることで探している言葉が見つかるのを望むかのように、華子はクッションの中で小さく身じろぎする。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3420
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_792e9b61:

    # ha "I… I was in an accident."
    ha "じ……事故に遭ったの"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3422
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_085f70ab:

    # hi "Accident? Just now? Are you all right?"
    hi "事故？　それって今？　元気じゃないか"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3427
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_0d38ccce:

    # "Hanako shakes her head, her hair flowing around her shoulders in wisps of amethyst on a background of pale and dark flesh."
    "華子は首を振り、その髪が青白く暗い肌を下地にして、紫色の束となって肩の周りに広がる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3432
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_88aaa4a3:

    # ha "N-no. When I was y-younger."
    ha "う、ううん。ち、小さいときに"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3436
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_8d4ce2bf:

    # "Realization crashes into me like a semi."
    "華子が言おうとしていることの意味が、俺の頭にセミトレーラーのごとく殺到する。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3438
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_38beb042:

    # ha "When I… when I was…"
    ha "私……私は昔……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3440
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_e8b16f5b:

    # hi "It's all right Hanako, you don't have to tell me anything if you don't want to…"
    hi "大丈夫だ華子。言いたくないことは言わなくていいんだぞ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3442
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_5bc16071:

    # "Again she shakes her head."
    "華子はもう一度首を振る。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3447
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_3b36a0d5:

    # ha "N-no. I want… I have to tell you."
    ha "ち、違うの。言いたい、言わなくちゃだめなの"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3454
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_e7a3777b:

    # ha "When I was young… I was in a fire."
    ha "私が小さかったとき……火事に遭ったの"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3456
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_81215d0d:

    # ha "M-my house b-burned down, and I nearly… I nearly didn't make it."
    ha "い、家は全焼して、私ももう少しで……もう少しで助からなかった"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3462
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_0faf065d:

    # ha "A-after that… I was alone…"
    ha "その後……私は一人になって……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3470
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_fe3d5e06:

    # "Hanako's eyes glisten in the dim light of the library, and I reach out to grasp her hand."
    "華子の瞳が薄暗い図書室の光にきらめいたのを見て、俺はその手を掴もうと手を伸ばす。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3472
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_acffb714:

    # hi "It's okay, Hanako. You don't have to keep going."
    hi "いいんだ華子。無理しなくていいから"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3477
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_64fa94c8:

    # ha "B-but… I have to…"
    ha "で、でも……言わないと……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3479
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_28ec15f7:

    # hi "Why? What brought this on?"
    hi "なんでだよ？　どうしてそこまでするんだ？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3484
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_6546120e:

    # ha "L-Last night Lilly t-told me about your heart…"
    ha "き、昨日の夜、リリーが久夫くんの心臓のこと、話してくれて……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3489
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_e266b502:

    # ha "A-and I… I didn't think it was f-fair."
    ha "そ、それで私……それじゃ、こ、公平じゃないって思って"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3491
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_c8114f15:

    # hi "Fair?"
    hi "公平？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3496
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_756e589a:

    # ha "T-that I knew about you b-but you didn't know about me…"
    ha "私は、ひ、久夫くんのこと知ってる、のに、久夫くんは私のこと知らない……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3498
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_50d4a94b:

    # "I squeeze Hanako's hand a little."
    "華子の手を少し強く握る。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3500
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_fb3ba6d5:

    # hi "Don't be silly. But yes, I have a heart condition."
    hi "ばかなこと言うなよ。だけどそうだな、俺は心臓の病気を持ってる"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3502
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_40ebfd87:

    # "I lean a little closer to Hanako."
    "俺は華子のほうに少し体を乗り出す。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3504
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_9bb46ab3:

    # hi "What I didn't tell Lilly is that I had my first attack when a girl confessed to me."
    hi "そのことだけど、リリーに言わなかったことがあるんだ。初めて病状が出たのって女の子に告白されたときだったんだよね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3506
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_0502808f:

    # "I smile a little to break the tension."
    "俺は二人の間の緊張をほぐすために微笑む。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3511
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_b6cc3c0b:

    # ha "R-really?"
    ha "ほ、本当に？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3513
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_43ca3443:

    # hi "Really. I haven't heard from her for a while though, so I guess it's all over."
    hi "ああ本当だ。でもそれから音沙汰が無いから、終わったんだと思う"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3515
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_6441e68b:

    # "I know it's all over. There's no other way to interpret what happened the last time I saw her. In some ways, not having heard from her again has helped me move on from that period of my life."
    "間違いなく終わっている。岩魚子と最後に会ったときの出来事は、それ以外に解釈のしようがない。それ以来連絡がなかったことは、ある意味で俺にとってあの日々から先に進む助けになっていた。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3517
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_4cf2653d:

    # hi "So now, we both know a little more about each other. But you don't have to talk about things if you don't want to."
    hi "さて、お互いに少しは知ってることが増えたな。でも言いたくないことは言わなくていいんだぞ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3519
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_2426c794:

    # "In fact, I feel a little bad even thinking about that whole incident. I can almost smell the hospital's disinfectant burning the back of my sinuses again."
    "実際、俺だってこれまであった出来事全てを思い出すと少々気分が悪くなる。鼻の裏側を燃やすような病院の消毒の臭いがフラッシュバックしてくるかのようだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3521
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_de5bd408:

    # "I imagine Hanako is going through the same thing now."
    "華子も今同じものを感じているだろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3525
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3528
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_8c19269f:

    # n "{vspace=60}When I was in the hospital I went to the burn ward once, and only once. I was bored, so I went for a walk through all of the wards."
    n "\n\n俺は入院していたとき一度、火傷患者の病棟に行ったことがある。本当に一度だけだけど。退屈を紛らわせるために、全ての病棟を歩き回っていたんだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3530
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_fdff8193:

    # n "I went through oncology and thought I could take it, but when I got to the burn ward I turned around and went back to my bed."
    n "腫瘍病棟を通り抜けたときは、耐えられると思ったけど、火傷病棟にたどり着いたとき、俺は回れ右をして自分のベッドに戻った。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3532
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_784965c1:

    # n "To think that Hanako would have spent months in a place like that, smelling nothing but corrupted skin, strong disinfectant and sterilized air."
    n "ただれた皮膚と強い消毒と殺菌の臭いだけが漂う、そんな場所で華子が何か月も過ごしていたのだろうと思うと。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3534
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_cf98c88d:

    # n "The really bad cases were kept in isolated pods that no foreign objects could enter. That would have meant no reading."
    n "本当に深刻なケースだと、外部から何も中に入らない隔離カプセルのようなものに入れられ続けることもある。つまり読書はできないってことだ。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3536
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_8a557bd7:

    # n "{vspace=30}I would have gone insane if I didn't have my books in the hospital."
    n "\nもし入院中に本がなかったら、俺は気が狂っていただろう。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3538
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_c5eebcd4:

    # n "And she said she was alone…"
    n "そして華子は『一人だった』と言っていた……"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3540
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_7afe38dd:

    # n "Did her parents die? I'll have to ask Lilly about it. I can imagine myself saying something dumb unintentionally."
    n "親は亡くなったのだろうか？　今度リリーに聞いておこう。じゃないと意図せず何かバカなことを口走って地雷を踏むのが目に見える。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3544
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3550
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_74c2ab5d:

    # ha "T-thank you, Hisao."
    ha "あ、ありがと、久夫くん"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3555
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_469d29e6:

    # ha "I… I haven't told many people about this."
    ha "こ……このこと、ほとんど人に言ったことないんだ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3557
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_a3366c17:

    # hi "To be honest, I haven't told many people about my… circumstances either."
    hi "正直言うと、俺も自分の……体のこと、ほとんど話したことないんだよね"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3562
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_7e647897:

    # ha "T-then I won't tell a-anyone either."
    ha "そ、それなら、私も誰にも言わない"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3564
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_a5f1a108:

    # hi "Deal."
    hi "じゃあ約束だ"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3568
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_45004422:

    # "I change my grip on Hanako's hand into a handshake as the warning bells chime through the window."
    "俺が華子の手を握る手を握手の形に変えたと同時に、窓の外から予鈴が聞こえてくる。"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3570
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_0b3aab3d:

    # hi "Well then, we'd better head back to class then, eh?"
    hi "よし、そろそろ教室に戻ったほうがいいな、大丈夫か？"

# game/script-a2-hanako.rpy:3575
translate jp a2_hanako_equivalent_exchange_ff70d1cd_1:

    # ha "S-sure."
    ha "う、うん"

